20giant%20American%20stocks%20have%20had%20a%20hell%20of%20a%20run%20on%20the%20back%20of%20AI%2C%20and%20that%20has%20certainly%20created%20the%20impression%20that%20it's%20game%20over.%20The%20problem%20is%20prices%20are%20incredibly%20high%20and%20basically%20the%20economy%20is%20beginning%20to%20unravel.%20So%20it's%20a%20head%20fake%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20hell%20of%20a%20head%20fake.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26quot%3BThe%20US%20equity%20market%2C%20led%20by%20the%20growth%20stocks%2C%20became%20a%20frenzy%20of%20meme%20starts%20and%20craziness%2C%20led%20incidentally%20by%20the%20biggest%20investment%20I%20ever%20made%20in%20a%20startup%2C%20QuantumScape.%20It%20came%20as%20a%20SPAC%2C%20which%20I%20hate%2C%20I%20think%20they%20should%20be%20illegal.%20This%20company%20that%20had%20four%20years%20before%20it%20had%20a%20product%20%E2%80%94%20forget%20profits%20or%20sales%20%E2%80%94%20was%20selling%20for%20more%20than%20General%20Motors%20or%20Panasonic.%20There%20was%20nothing%20at%20that%20scale%20in%201929%20or%202000.%20This%20was%20probably%20one%20of%20the%20great%20speculative%20events%20of%20all%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20be%20very%20careful%20with%20real%20estate.%20All%20over%20the%20world%2C%20the%20last%2020%20years%20of%20declining%20mortgage%20rates%20have%20driven%20real%20estate%20to%20really%20crushing%20high%20multiples%20of%20family%20income%2C%20so%20high%20that%20young%20people%20can't%20buy%20a%20house.%20So%20I%20wouldn't%20touch%20real%20estate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20very%20nervous%20about%20the%20economy.%20I'm%20very%20nervous%20about%20an%20eventual%20financial%20trouble.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20climate-change%20stocks.%20They%20will%20have%20an%20incredible%20top-line%20revenue%20growth%2C%20driving%20forward%20like%20Tesla%20and%20electric%20vehicles%20versus%20dopey%20VWs%20and%20old-fashioned%20cars.%20This%20is%20the%20area%20with%20the%20wind%20in%20your%20sails%2C%20and%20to%20fight%20it%20would%20be%20a%20terrible%20mistake.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E7.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26quot%3BIt's%20woken%20everybody%20up%2C%20and%20it%20was%20like%20dealing%20with%20sleepwalkers%20before%20that.%20When%20you%20see%20something%20terrible%20coming%C2%A0down%20the%20pipeline%20and%20nobody%20taking%20it%20seriously%2C%20that%20is%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20nightmare.%20That%20phase%C2%A0at%20least%20is%20over.%26quot%3B%20(Grantham%20was%20welcoming%20increased%20awareness%20and%20acceptance%20of%20climate%20change.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E8.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26quot%3BIt%20will%20dominate%20the%20portfolios%20of%20the%20rest%20of%20your%20lives.%20It%20doesn't%20mean%20there%20won't%20be%20financial%C2%A0problems%2C%20it%20doesn't%20mean%20there%20won't%20be%20bubbles.%20But%20it%20will%20be%20the%20sector%20of%20the%20economy%20that%20drives%20more%20growth%20than%20anything%20else.%26quot%3B%20(Grantham%20was%20referring%20to%20companies%20working%20to%20combat%20climate%20change.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E9.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26quot%3BBear%20in%20mind%2C%20every%20commodity%20is%20a%20royal%20pain%20to%20own%20because%20it%20has%20totally%20unpredictable%20and%20shocking%20drops%20along%20the%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E10.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26quot%3BThe%20Fed%20and%20the%20economic%20establishment%2C%20the%20financial%20establishment%2C%20they've%20always%20underestimated%20the%20probability%20of%20a%20recession.%20They%20always%20say%20everything%20will%20be%20fine.%20This%20is%20not%20unusual%2C%20it's%20absolutely%20inevitable%2C%20and%20here%20they%20go%20again.%20It%20would%20be%20unique%20if%20we%20don't%20have%20an%20extended%20problem%20with%20the%20economy.%3Cbr%3E(Grantham%20pegged%20the%20probability%20of%20a%20recession%20in%20the%20next%2018%20months%20at%20about%2070%25.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeremy-grantham-quotes-stocks-recession-housing-market-bubble-tesla-economy-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694950501000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F600ee2f17e47190011cb901c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fjeremy-grantham-quotes-stocks-recession-housing-market-bubble-tesla-economy-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jeremy%20Grantham%20warned%20the%20AI%20craze%20won't%20stop%20the%20bubble%20in%20stocks%20from%20bursting%2C%20and%20pegged%20the%20odds%20of%20a%20recession%20by%20early%202025%20at%2070%25.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tmohamed%40insider.com%20(Theron%20Mohamed)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fjeremy-grantham-quotes-stocks-recession-housing-market-bubble-tesla-economy-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Madhu%20Chopra%20wishes%20Nick%20on%20his%20b'day%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694950485000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103733986%2Cimgsize-62058.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fpriyanka-chopras-mother-madhu-has-the-sweetest-birthday-wish-for-her-gorgeous-son-in-law-nick-jonas%2Farticleshow%2F103733986.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103733986.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20caption%2C%20Madhu%20Chopra%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CWishing%20my%20gorgeous%20son%20in%20law%20Nick%20a%20very%20happy%20birthday%20with%20a%20red%20heart%20and%20party%20popper%20emoji%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Centre%20Releases%20Disability%20Data%20Sans%20Socio-Economic%20Categories%20Citing%20Issues%20With%20Data%20'Quality'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F28103733%2Fimages.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Union%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20not%20release%20any%20socio-economic%20data%20it%20had%20collected%20while%20registering%20persons%20with%20disabilities%20for%20its%20Unique%20Disability%20ID%20(UDID)%20cards%20in%20the%20last%20six%20years%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fgovt-shelves-socio-economic-data-of-pwds-as-disability-database-goes-online%2Farticle67312174.ece%5C%22%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Social%20Justice%20and%20Empowerment%20has%20justified%20the%20move%20by%20questioning%20the%20%E2%80%9Cquality%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20socio-economic%20data%20collected.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInformation%20on%20categories%20like%20caste%2C%20level%20of%20education%2C%20employment%20status%2C%20income%20(personal%20and%20family)%20and%20marital%20status%20of%20persons%20with%20disabilities%20has%20been%20shelved%20with%20officials%20saying%20that%20the%20focus%20of%20the%20form%20was%20always%20to%20collect%20disability%20data%20and%20hence%20all%20other%20fields%20were%20made%20optional%20which%20led%20to%20many%20skipping%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERajesh%20Aggarwal%2C%20Secretary%2C%20Department%20of%20Empowerment%20of%20Persons%20with%20Disabilities%20(DEPwD)%20of%20the%20Social%20Justice%20Ministry%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20data%20are%20not%20being%20released%20because%20of%20quality%20issues.%E2%80%9D%20When%20asked%20if%20the%20department%20intends%20to%20pursue%20collecting%20socio-economic%20data%20for%20future%20UDID%20registrations%2C%20Aggarwal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fgovt-shelves-socio-economic-data-of-pwds-as-disability-database-goes-online%2Farticle67312174.ece%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20basic%20purpose%20of%20the%20form%20is%20to%20get%20a%20disability%20certificate%E2%80%A6%20and%20also%2C%20we%20cannot%20afford%20to%20make%20the%20form%20too%20lengthy%20by%20seeking%20information%20we%20cannot%20verify.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20DEPwD%20earlier%20this%20week%20published%20what%20it%20called%20aggregated%20data%20from%20the%20around%2094%20lakh%20UDID%20registrations%2C%20minus%20the%20socio-economic%20data%2C%20with%20a%20statement%20alongside%20spelling%20out%20the%20objective%20of%20the%20project%20%E2%80%93%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccreate%20a%20national%20database%20for%20all%20Persons%20with%20Disabilities%20(PwDs)%20along%20with%20their%20socio-economic%20details%E2%80%9D%20so%20that%20policy-making%20and%20interventions%20can%20be%20targeted%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20has%20not%20officially%20disclosed%20the%20exact%20number%20of%20people%20who%20filled%20in%20the%20socio-economic%20fields.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Funion-government-defends-decision-to-remove-questions-on-disability-from-nfhs-6%5C%22%3EUnion%20Government%20Defends%20Decision%20to%20Remove%20Questions%20on%20Disability%20From%20NFHS-6%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOther%20heads%20under%20which%20the%20government%20chose%20not%20to%20publish%20data%20are%20the%20fields%20of%20personal%20and%20family%20income%20(spouse%20and%20father)%2C%20whether%20they%20were%20Below%20Poverty%20Line%2C%20employment%20status%2C%20occupation%2C%20socio-economic%20category%20(SC%2FST%2FOBC%2FGeneral)%2C%20and%20level%20of%20education.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20senior%20government%20official%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20marital%20status%20%E2%80%93%20only%20about%2015%25%20of%20those%20registered%20have%20filled%20it%20in.%20It%20is%20not%20enough%20data%20to%20be%20significant.%20Again%2C%20information%20on%20income%2C%20just%2040%25%20have%20filled%20it%20in.%20The%20department%20has%20no%20way%20to%20verify%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20this%20information%20is%20accurate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20official%20aware%20of%20the%20programme%E2%80%99s%20implementation%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20enough%E2%80%9D%20people%20had%20responded%20to%20fields%20such%20as%20education%20and%20socio-economic%20category%20either%2C%20adding%20this%20was%20among%20the%20primary%20reasons%20for%20discounting%20this%20data.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20medical%20data%20and%20disability-related%20data%20are%20high-quality%20because%20they%20were%20verified%20by%20doctors.%20And%20since%20the%20purpose%20was%20to%20register%20people%20for%20disability%20certificates%20to%20make%20them%20eligible%20for%20the%20department%E2%80%99s%20schemes%2C%20only%20those%20fields%20were%20made%20mandatory%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20official%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20even%20among%20the%20benefits%20offered%20by%20the%20DEPwD%2C%20four%20of%20the%20seven%20initiatives%20are%20related%20to%20special%20education%20and%20vocational%20training%20programmes%2C%20skill%20training%20and%20scholarships.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20data%20released%20by%20the%20government%20includes%20district-wise%2C%20gender-wise%2C%20disability%20type-wise%20and%20age-wise%20information%20and%20will%20be%20updated%20every%20quarter%2C%20the%20government%20has%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20had%20added%20that%20the%20UDID%20database%20was%20also%20meant%20to%20help%20design%20accessible%20websites%20and%20applications%20and%20%E2%80%9Cconnect%20PwDs%20to%20digital%20India%E2%80%9D.%20However%2C%20nowhere%20in%20the%20UDID%20form%20is%20any%20section%20seeking%20information%20on%20existing%20computer%2C%20mobile%2C%20and%20Internet%20usage%20among%20PwDs%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20has%20already%20been%20under%20attack%20from%20experts%2C%20activists%2C%20and%20Opposition%20leaders%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Funion-government-defends-decision-to-remove-questions-on-disability-from-nfhs-6%5C%22%3Edropping%20disability-related%20questions%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20forms%20issued%20for%20the%20sixth%20round%20of%20the%20National%20Family%20Health%20Survey%20earlier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694950426000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F28103733%2Fimages.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcentre-releases-disability-data-sans-socio-economic-categories-citing-issues-with-data-quality%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20has%20already%20been%20under%20attack%20for%20dropping%20disability-related%20questions%20from%20the%20sixth%20round%20of%20the%20National%20Family%20Health%20Survey%20earlier.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mohammed%20Siraj%20Lights%20Up%20Asia%20Cup%20Final%20With%20Fastest%205-Wicket%20Haul%20In%20ODIs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20pacer%20%3Ca%20tit