a-cup-2023%2Findia-vs-sri-lanka-mohammed-siraj-lights-up-asia-cup-final-with-rapid-five-wicket-haul-watch-4398051%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Findia-vs-sri-lanka-mohammed-siraj-lights-up-asia-cup-final-with-rapid-five-wicket-haul-watch-4398051%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Findia-vs-sri-lanka-mohammed-siraj-lights-up-asia-cup-final-with-rapid-five-wicket-haul-watch-4398051%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hemant%20Soren%20Challenges%20Probe%20Agency%20Summons%2C%20Supreme%20Court%20To%20Hear%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJharkhand%20Chief%20Minister%20Hemant%20Soren%20today%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20challenging%20summons%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case.%20The%20Chief%20Minister%20had%20last%20month%20confronted%20the%20federal%20agency%20asking%20it%20to%20withdraw%20the%20summon%20against%20him%20or%20else%20he%20would%20take%20legal%20action.%20The%20top%20court%20will%20hear%20his%20case%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHemant%20Soren%20has%20been%20summoned%20by%20the%20ED%20for%20September%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCentre%20is%20using%20ED%20to%20target%20opposition%20leaders%20who%20are%20not%20towing%20the%20lines%20of%20the%20government%20and%20this%20targeting%20has%20picked%20up%20pace%20with%20the%20date%20of%20General%20Elections%20fast%20approaching%20and%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20INDIA%20against%20the%20ruling%20NDA%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr%20Soren%20has%20contended%20in%20his%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20repeated%20summoning%20under%20the%20garb%20of%20investigation%20under%20the%20PMLA%20of%20the%20properties%20owned%2C%20possessed%20and%20occupied%20by%20the%20Petitioner%20and%20the%20source%20of%20its%20acquisition%2C%20which%20information%20and%20material%20is%20already%20in%20the%20possession%20of%20the%20ED%20and%20with%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20is%20nothing%20but%20a%20ruse%20to%20harass%2C%20browbeat%20and%20intimidate%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20Central%20Government%20and%20a%20complete%20misuse%20of%20the%20powers%20by%20the%20ED%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20probe%20agency%20had%20last%20month%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjharkhand-illegal-mining-case-money-laundering-probe-chief-minister-hemant-soren-summoned-by-enforcement-directorate-for-questioning-in-money-launderi-4280065%5C%22%3Easked%20Mr%20Soren%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20join%20its%20investigation%20in%20the%20case.%C2%A0The%20Chief%20Minister%20had%20then%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frefer-to-documents-hemant-soren-to-probe-agency-over-summons-4298236%5C%22%3Ein%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20central%20probe%20agency%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20he%20has%20provided%20all%20necessary%20documents%20and%20information.%20If%20the%20ED%20needs%20any%20information%2C%20it%20can%20refer%20to%20the%20documents%2C%20he%20added.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EHemant%20Soren%20is%20being%20investigated%20over%20allegations%20of%20money%20laundering%20linked%20to%20an%20illegal%20mining%20case%20in%20Jharkhand's%20Sahebganj%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20who%20is%20also%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20state%20mining%20ministry%2C%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20violating%20election%20rules%20by%20giving%20himself%20a%20mining%20lease%20in%202021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMr%20Soren%20has%2C%20however%2C%20denied%20any%20wrongdoing%20and%20alleged%20a%20larger%20conspiracy%20to%20%26quot%3Bharass%20a%20tribal%20leader%26quot%3B.%20He%20said%20that%20central%20agencies%20are%20targeting%20him%20because%20he%20is%20not%20aligning%20with%20the%20central%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20has%20also%20mentioned%20that%20he%20has%20provided%20the%20details%20of%20his%20movable%20and%20immovable%20assets%20to%20CBI%20in%20an%20enquiry%20directed%20by%20Lokpal%20against%20his%20father%20Shibu%20Soren%20in%202020.%20ED%20may%20obtain%20the%20details%20from%20CBI.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20skipped%20the%20ED's%20summons%20in%20November%20and%20went%20to%20Chhattisgarh%20to%20attend%20a%20dance%20festival%20instead.%20Speaking%20about%20his%20decision%20to%20skip%20his%20questioning%20and%20attend%20the%20festival%20that%20was%20scheduled%20in%20advance%2C%20Mr%20Soren%20objected%20to%20what%20he%20alleged%20was%20a%20short%20notice%20from%20the%20probe%20agency%20to%20appear.%20%26quot%3BAre%20we%20thieves%20or%20anti-socials%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked%20while%20speaking%20to%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694950260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Fuobh5lkg_hemant-soren-pti_625x300_04_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhemant-soren-files-appeal-in-supreme-court-challenges-enforcement-directorates-summons-in-money-laundering-case-4398007%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jharkhand%20Chief%20Minister%20Hemant%20Soren%20today%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20challenging%20summons%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhemant-soren-files-appeal-in-supreme-court-challenges-enforcement-directorates-summons-in-money-laundering-case-4398007%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhemant-soren-files-appeal-in-supreme-court-challenges-enforcement-directorates-summons-in-money-laundering-case-4398007%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhemant-soren-files-appeal-in-supreme-court-challenges-enforcement-directorates-summons-in-money-laundering-case-4398007%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Alia's%20car%20gets%20mobbed%20by%20a%20group%20of%20women%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694950188000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103733894%2Cimgsize-53198.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fa-viral-video-shows-alia-bhatts-car-getting-mobbed-by-a-group-of-women-at-a-traffic-signal-fans-react%2Farticleshow%2F103733894.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103733894.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EA%20video%20circulating%20on%20social%20media%20shows%20a%20group%20of%20women%20peering%20into%20an%20SUV%2C%20rumored%20to%20belong%20to%20actress%20Alia%20Bhatt%2C%20before%20it%20drives%20off.%20The%20incident%20has%20sparked%20comments%20about%20celebrities'%20need%20for%20personal%20space%20and%20the%20public's%20perception%20of%20them.%20Bhatt%20and%20her%20husband%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%20recently%20returned%20to%20Mumbai%20after%20their%20film%20'Rocky%20Aur%20Rani%20Kii%20Prem%20Kahaani'%20received%20positive%20reviews.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SBI%20To%20Send%20Chocolates%20To%20Borrowers%20Likely%20To%20Default%20On%20Repayments%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20nation's%20largest%20lender%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20is%20adopting%20a%20novel%20way%20to%20ensure%20timely%20repayments%2C%20especially%20by%20its%20retail%20borrowers%2C%20by%20greeting%20those%20likely%20to%20default%20on%20monthly%20installments%20with%20a%20pack%20of%20chocolates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20bank%2C%20it%20has%20been%20found%20that%20a%20borrower%20who%20is%20planning%20to%20default%20will%20not%20answer%20a%20reminder%20call%20from%20the%20bank.%20So%20the%20best%20way%20is%20to%20meet%20them%20at%20their%20homes%20unannounced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%2C%20aimed%20at%20ensuring%20better%20collections%2C%20comes%20amidst%20rising%20level%20of%20retail%20lending%20in%20the%20system%20coupled%20with%20increasing%20delinquency%20levels%20on%20the%20back%20of%20the%20upward%20movement%20in%20the%20interest%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESBI's%20retail%20loan%20book%20grew%20over%2016.46%20per%20cent%20to%20Rs%2012%2C04%2C279%20crore%20in%20the%20June%202023%20quarter%20from%20Rs%2010%2C34%2C111%20crore%20in%20the%20year-ago%20period%2C%20making%20it%20the%20largest%20asset%20class%20for%20the%20lender%20whose%20total%20book%20stood%20at%20Rs%2033%2C03%2C731%20crore%2C%20growing%20at%2013.9%20per%20cent%20on-year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%20for%20the%20entire%20system%2C%20the%20double-digit%20loan%20growth%20of%20around%2016%20per%20cent%20has%20been%20led%20by%20retail%20loans%20only.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20two%20fintechs%20which%20use%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20we%20are%20piloting%20a%20novel%20way%20of%20reminding%20our%20retail%20borrowers%20of%20their%20repayment%20obligations.%20While%20one%20is%20doing%20conciliation%20with%20borrowers%2C%20the%20other%20is%20alerting%20us%20on%20the%20propensity%20of%20a%20borrower%20to%20default.%20And%20to%20such%20borrowers%20who%20are%20likely%20to%20default%2C%20the%20representatives%20from%20this%20fintech%20will%20visit%20them%2C%20carrying%20a%20pack%20of%20chocolates%20for%20each%20of%20them%2C%20and%20remind%20them%20of%20the%20forthcoming%20EMIs%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwini%20Kumar%20Tewari%2C%20managing%20director%20in-charge%20of%20risk%2C%20compliance%20and%20stressed%20assets%20at%20SBI%2C%20said%20over%20the%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Tewari%2C%20this%20novel%20method%20of%20carrying%20a%20pack%20of%20chocolates%20and%20personally%20visiting%20them%20is%20adopted%20because%20it%20has%20been%20found%20that%20a%20borrower%20who%20is%20planning%20to%20default%20will%20not%20answer%20a%20reminder%20call%20from%20the%20bank.%20So%20the%20best%20way%20is%20to%20meet%20them%20at%20their%20own%20homes%20unannounced%20and%20surprise%20them.%20And%20so%20far%2C%20the%20success%20rate%20has%20been%20overwhelming%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETewari%20refused%20to%20name%20the%20fintechs%20saying%20the%20move%20is%20just%20at%20the%20pilot%20stage%20and%20has%20been%20put%20into%20place%20just%20about%2015%20days%20back%20and%20%26quot%3Bif%20successful%2C%20we%20will%20formally%20announce%20it%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20also%20talking%20to%20a%20few%20other%20fintechs%20to%20improve%20our%20collection%20efficiencies%20and%20hopefully%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%2C%20we%20will%20have%20formally%20tied%20up%20with%20at%20least%20half%20of%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20want%20to%20continue%20the%20pilot%20for%20at%20least%20four%20to%20five%20months.%26quot%3B%20SBI's%20over%20Rs%2012%20lakh%20crore%20of%20retail%20book%20consists%20of%20personal%2C%20auto%2C%20home%20and%20education%20loans.%20With%20a%20home%20loan%20book%20of%20over%20Rs%206.3%20lakh%20crore%20as%20of%20June%2C%20SBI%20is%20the%20largest%20mortgage%20lender%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694949960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Fqtdflddg_sbi-reuters-generic_625x300_05_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsbi-to-send-chocolates-to-borrowers-likely-to-default-on-monthly-repayments-4398139%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20nation's%20largest%20lender%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20is%20adopting%20a%20novel%20way%20to%20ensure%20timely%20repayments%2C%20especially%20by%20its%20retail%20borrowers%2C%20by%20greeting%20those%20likely%20to%20default%20on%20mon