17-at-2.24.53-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20As%20Project%20Cheetah%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20ambitious%20intercontinental%20cheetah%20translocation%20programme%2C%20enters%20its%20second%20year%20on%20Sunday%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20plans%20to%20import%20more%20big%20cats%20that%20do%20not%20have%20thick%20winter%20coats.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20year%20on%20his%20birthday%2C%20September%2017%2C%20in%20a%20spectacle%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20turned%20the%20cheetah%20translocation%20project%20which%20had%20been%20in%20the%20works%20for%20a%20decade%2C%20into%20a%20personal%20project%20and%20released%20eight%20cheetahs%20from%20Namibia%20into%20the%20Kuno%20National%20Park%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20February%2018%2C%20the%20second%20batch%20of%20cheetahs%20arrived%20in%20India%20from%20South%20Africa.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20the%2020%20African%20cheetahs%20brought%20from%20Namibia%20and%20South%20Africa%2C%20six%20adults%20and%20three%20cubs%20have%20died.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ES.P%20Yadav%2C%20Additional%20Director%20General%20of%20Forests%20at%20the%20Environment%20Ministry%2C%20said%20that%20one%20of%20the%20major%20challenges%20faced%20in%20the%20first%20year%20of%20managing%20cheetahs%20in%20India%20was%20the%20%E2%80%9Cunexpected%20development%E2%80%9D%20of%20winter%20coats%20in%20some%20cheetahs%20during%20the%20Indian%20summer%20and%20monsoon%2C%20in%20anticipation%20of%20the%20African%20winter%20(June%20to%20September).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSome%20cheetahs%20did%20not%20develop%20winter%20coats%20and%20remained%20infection-free.%20They%20are%20better%20suited%20to%20Indian%20conditions.%20Therefore%2C%20in%20our%20next%20cheetah%20import%2C%20we%20will%20be%20very%20careful%20in%20animal%20selection.%20We%20will%20prefer%20animals%20that%20either%20do%20not%20develop%20winter%20coats%20or%20develop%20thinner%20ones%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20to%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYadav%20said%20that%20the%20winter%20coats%20along%20with%20high%20humidity%2C%20temperatures%20caused%20itching%20in%20the%20animals%20and%20subsequently%20led%20to%20bruising%20and%20exposed%20skin%20where%20flies%20laid%20eggs%20resulting%20in%20maggot%20infestations%2C%20infections%20and%20septicemia%20leading%20to%20deaths.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20project%2C%20which%20has%20since%20been%20mired%20in%20controversy%20since%20the%20beginning%2C%20enters%20its%20second%20year%2C%20Yadav%20said%20that%20this%20time%20the%20focus%20will%20be%20on%20breeding%20cheetahs%20on%20Indian%20soil.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20thing%20that%20comes%20to%20my%20mind%20is%20the%20breeding%20of%20cheetahs.%20And%20if%20we%20can%20expect%20more%20litter%2C%20the%20cubs%20born%20on%20Indian%20soil%20can%20better%20adapt%20to%20Indian%20situations.%20Once%20the%20breeding%20takes%20place%2C%20we%20will%20understand%20how%20the%20population%20will%20behave%20in%20our%20country.%20So%2C%20the%20main%20thing%20next%20year%20will%20be%20more%20cubs%20on%20the%20soil%20of%20Bharat%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECheetah%20deaths%20mired%20in%20controversy%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20government%20is%20planning%20to%20import%20and%20breed%20more%20cheetahs%2C%20the%20project%20itself%20has%20been%20mired%20in%20controversy%20because%20of%20the%20deaths%20of%20the%20big%20cats%20on%20Indian%20soil.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20August%202%20this%20year%2C%20Tiblisi%20%E2%80%93%20aka%20Dhatri%2C%20a%20female%20brought%20to%20Kuno%20from%20Namibia%20was%20found%20dead%2C%20becoming%20the%20the%20sixth%20adult%20cheetah%20to%20die%2C%20from%20the%20cheetahs%20brought%20as%20part%20of%20Project%20Cheetah.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrior%20to%20that%20two%20males%20Tejas%20and%20Suraj%20died%20on%20July%2011%20and%2014.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20experts%20on%20the%20Cheetah%20Project%20Steering%20Committee%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fninth-cheetah-dies-in-kuno-national-park%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ethat%20the%20animals%20died%20due%20to%20radio%20collar-caused%20infections%2C%20the%20National%20Tiger%20Conservation%20Authority%20(NTCA%2C%20which%20implements%20Project%20Cheetah)%20claimed%20that%20all%20cheetahs%20died%20due%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fauthorities-say-recent-cheetah-deaths-due-to-natural-causes-mp-chief-wildlife-warden-transferred%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cnatural%20causes%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20very%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELater%20on%20July%2020%20the%20Environment%2C%20Forest%20and%20Climate%20Change%20ministry%20in%20a%20reply%20in%20parliament%20said%20that%20three%20cheetahs%20%E2%80%93%20Daksha%2C%20Tejas%20and%20Suraj%20%E2%80%93%20had%20died%20due%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctraumatic%20shock%E2%80%9D%20without%20mentioning%20what%20caused%20the%20traumatic%20shock.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20three%20cubs%20died%20from%20heat%20stress%2C%20according%20to%20official%20records.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20experts%2C%20several%20deaths%20could%20have%20been%20avoided.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20India%20we%20had%20dedicated%20veterinary%20support%20and%20intensive%20post%20release%20monitoring.%20It%20was%20assumed%20that%20these%20two%20factors%20would%20minimise%20the%20mortality%20rate%20next%20to%20zero%2C%20at%20least%20in%20the%20initial%20part%20of%20the%20project%20till%20the%20animals%20are%20released%20in%20the%20wild%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Adrian%20Tordiffe%2C%20a%20veterinary%20wildlife%20specialist%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Pretoria%20and%20a%20former%20foreign%20consultant%20on%20the%20project%2C%20told%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fdeaths-cast-shadow-over-project-cheetah-anniversary-2688528%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20Deccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20it%20turned%20out%2C%20most%20of%20them%20died%20in%20the%20acclimatisation%20camp.%20This%20was%20a%20setback.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20project%20has%20also%20remained%20controversial%20because%20of%20the%20lack%20of%20information%20being%20shared%20with%20experts%20as%20per%20their%20claims.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fproject-cheetah-media-gag-order%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Egag%20order%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Ewas%20also%20issued%20on%20officials%20involved%20in%20Project%20Cheetah%20which%20prevents%20them%20from%20speaking%20to%20the%20press%20on%20any%20information%20regarding%20the%20project.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20July%2C%20Tordiffe%20had%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fproject-cheetah-deaths-radio-collar-infections%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20communication%20between%20the%20Indian%20and%20South%20African%20teams%20was%20a%20concern.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20issue%20was%20the%20level%20of%20veterinary%20care%20available%20at%20Kuno%3B%20another%20was%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20senior%20scientist%20at%20Kuno%20to%20coordinate%20the%20management%20and%20monitoring%20of%20the%20animals%20after%20scientist%20Y.V.%20Jhala%20%E2%80%93%20who%20was%20leading%20the%20project%20on%20the%20ground%20%E2%80%93%20was%20forced%20to%20retire%2C%20he%20had%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20mortality%20from%20factors%20that%20could%20have%20been%20avoided%20with%20better%20supervision%2C%20expertise%2C%20and%20coordination%20with%20experts%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20Jhala%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%9CPrestige%20issue%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20July%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20questioned%20the%20Union%20government%20about%20the%20deaths%20of%20big%20cats%20and%20asked%20why%20it%20was%20such%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fprestige-issue-supreme-court-cheetah-deaths%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cprestige%20issue%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20It%20also%20asked%20why%20the%20cheetahs%20were%20all%20released%20in%20Kuno%20National%20Park%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20not%20spread%20out%20across%20sites.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Union%20in%20its%20affidavit%20to%20the%20court%20told%20the%20apex%20court%20that%20the%20deaths%20are%20%E2%80%9Ctroubling%E2%80%9D%20but%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20unduly%20alarming%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20reply%20was%20filed%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20asked%20for%20a%20detailed%20affidavit%20explaining%20the%20reasons%20for%20the%20cheetah%20deaths%2C%20and%20the%20remedial%20measures%20being%20taken%2C%20be%20submitted.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20centre%20also%20said%20that%20a%20provisional%20diagnosis%20of%20the%20cheetah%20deaths%20%E2%80%9Cpoints%20towards%20natural%20causes%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694940954000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F17142504%2FScreenshot-2023-09-17-at-2.24.53-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fon-its-one-year-anniversary-memories-of-nine-deaths-hang-over-project-cheetah%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20officials%2C%20one%20of%20the%20major%20challenges%20faced%20in%20the%20first%20