%20(DMRC)%20at%20the%20station.%C2%A0%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20high-speed%20corridor%20has%20been%20extended%20from%20Dwarka%20Sector%2021%20station%20to%20the%20Yashobhoomi%20Dwarka%20Sector%2025%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nearly%202-kilometre-long%20extension%20will%20connect%20Dwarka%20Sector%2021%20and%20India%20International%20Convention%20Centre.%C2%A0%26quot%3BWith%20the%20addition%20of%20this%20section%2C%20the%20total%20length%20of%20the%20Airport%20Express%20Line%20from%20New%20Delhi%20to%20Yashobhoomi%20Dwarka%20Sector-25%20will%20be%2024.9%20km%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20DMRC%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20inaugurating%20the%20Airport%20Express%20line%2C%20PM%20Modi%20unveiled%20the%20International%20Convention%20and%20Expo%20Centre%20(IICC)%2C%20also%20called%20'Yashobhoomi'%20in%20Dwarka.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20convention%20centre%2C%20built%20across%20more%20than%2073%2C000%20square%20metres%2C%20has%2015%20convention%20rooms%2C%20including%20the%20main%20auditorium%2C%20the%20grand%20ballroom%20and%2013%20meeting%20rooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20auditorium%20has%20an%20innovative%20automated%20seating%20system%20which%20converts%20the%20flat%20floor%20into%20an%20auditorium%20style%20tiered%20seating.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694938980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F72asdgb8_pm-modi_625x300_17_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-turns-73-pm-modi-birthday-pm-modis-metro-ride-on-his-birthday-selfies-with-passengers-4397491%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20took%20a%20ride%20in%20Delhi%20Metro%20after%20inaugurating%20the%20extension%20of%20the%20Airport%20Express%20line%20in%20Dwarka.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-turns-73-pm-modi-birthday-pm-modis-metro-ride-on-his-birthday-selfie