0began%20kicking%20in.%20A%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India-led%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20found%20itself%20having%20to%20consider%20the%20quantum%20of%20relief%20it%20could%20provide%20against%20harassment%20and%20coercion%20to%20the%20Editors%20Guild%20of%20India%2C%20the%20premier%20forum%20of%20professional%20journalists%20in%20India.%20A%20most%20consequential%20opportunity%20to%20roll%20back%20the%20gathering%20tide%20against%20a%20free%20media%20and%2C%20by%20extension%2C%20against%20the%20practices%20and%20protocols%20of%20democracy%20provided%20for%20in%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fegi-condemns-manipur-police-fir-against-its-members%5C%22%3Eapex%20court%20was%20called%20upon%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20decide%20whether%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fmanipur-police-files-fir-against-editors-guild-fact-finding-team-cites-revoked-sec-66a%5C%22%3Ebunch%20of%20FIRs%20filed%20in%20Manipur%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20the%20Guild%20should%20be%20quashed.%20Criminal%20proceedings%20were%20sought%20to%20be%20initiated%20against%20the%20Guild%20for%20sending%20an%20inquiry%20team%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Feditors-guild-fact-finding-report-manipur-media-meitei-biren-internet%5C%22%3Epublishing%20a%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20how%20(in)adequately%20the%20media%20had%20performed%20in%20reporting%20the%20ethnic%20conflict%20in%20Manipur.%20This%20attempted%20coercion%20was%20unprecedented.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20individual%20reporters%20have%20been%20subjected%20to%20harassment%2C%20mostly%20by%20right-wing%20partisans%20who%20slap%20frivolous%20cases%20on%20journalists%20and%20newspapers%20%E2%80%93%20and%2C%20in%20these%20times%20of%20extreme%20partisanship%20the%20police%20and%20the%20judiciary%20at%20the%20local%20level%20have%20been%20all%20too%20eager%20to%20be%20a%20complicit%20in%20these%20rites%20of%20intimidation%20and%20coercion.%20But%20it%20was%20the%20first%20time%20that%20a%20professional%20organisation%20was%20sought%20to%20be%20prosecuted%20for%20expressing%20an%20opinion%20on%20the%20lack%20of%20professionalism%20by%20the%20media%20fraternity%20in%20Manipur.%20A%20defining%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22281%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F04192003%2Fstatecraft.png%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-237577%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22233%5C%22%3ELet%20us%20step%20back%20a%20bit.%20In%20early%201981%2C%20Gujarat%20got%20engulfed%20in%20a%20vicious%20caste%20war%2C%20in%20which%20the%20Dalits%20found%20themselves%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20from%20savarna%20groups.%C2%A0%20There%20were%20charges%20of%20bias%20and%20distortions%20in%20the%20Gujarati%20press%20%E2%80%93%20a%20media%20that%20was%20controlled%20almost%20entirely%20by%20the%20upper%20caste%20journalists%20and%20owners.%20The%20Editors%E2%80%99%20Guild%20of%20India%2C%20in%20its%20collective%20professional%20wisdom%2C%20decided%20that%20the%20facts%20needed%20to%20be%20investigated%20and%20ascertained.%20A%20four-member%20team%2C%20consisting%20of%20B.G.%20Verghese%2C%20Inder%20Malhotra%2C%20Mahendra%20Desai%20and%20K.%20Narendra%2C%20visited%20Gujarat%20and%20produced%20a%20professional%20analysis%2C%20cogently%20titled%20%3Cem%3EA%20Mirror%20Cracked%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20report%20concluded%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Gujarati%20media%20took%20sides%20and%20published%20unverified%20reports%20in%20poster%20headlines%2C%20adding%20fuel%20to%20the%20fires.%20Perspective%20was%20lost.%E2%80%9D%20And%2C%20as%20Verghese%20recalled%2C%20in%20his%20book%2C%20%3Cem%3EFirst%20Draft%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Guild%20team%20hoped%20that%20the%20Gujarati%20press%20would%20look%20inwards%20and%20institute%20corrective%20measures.%20Regrettably%2C%20the%20same%20weaknesses%20were%20to%20show%20up%2C%20in%20an%20even%20worse%20form%2C%20in%202002.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Police%20%E2%80%98Excesses%E2%80%99%20Under%20Scanner%20in%20ABP%20Reporter%20Debmalya%20Bagchi%E2%80%99s%20Arrest%20in%20Bengal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpolice-excesses-under-scanner-in-abp-reporter-debmalya-bagchis-arrest-in-bengal%5C%22%3EPolice%20%E2%80%98Excesses%E2%80%99%20Under%20Scanner%20in%20ABP%20Reporter%20Debmalya%20Bagchi%E2%80%99s%20Arrest%20in%20Bengal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESections%20of%20the%20Gujarati%20press%20were%20obviously%20not%20pleased%20with%20the%20Guild%E2%80%99s%20report%20and%20expressed%20their%20dissent.%20But%20there%20were%20no%20attempts%20to%20visit%20vengeance%20upon%20the%20team%20members%20or%20the%20Guild.%20No%20FIRs%20were%20filed%3B%20the%20chief%20minister%20did%20not%20hold%20a%20press%20conference%20to%20denounce%20the%20Guild%20and%20its%20members.%20It%20remained%20a%20conversation%20within%20the%20journalistic%20fraternity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20an%20earnest%20effort%20by%20a%20professional%20body%20of%20journalists%20to%20try%20to%20initiate%20introspection%20among%20the%20entire%20journalistic%20fraternity%2C%20not%20just%20in%20Gujarat.%20As%20the%20country%20entered%20the%20decades%20of%20armed%20contestations%2C%20reporting%20from%20conflict%20zones%20became%20complex%20and%20hazardous.%20It%20was%20vitally%20important%20that%20the%20media%2C%20both%20as%20a%20democratic%20institution%20and%20as%20a%20modern%20professional%20organisation%2C%20should%20try%20to%20prescribe%20good%20practices%20and%20proscribe%20not%20so%20healthy%20ones.%20And%20that%20remains%20a%20work%20in%20progress.%20Ask%20any%20police%20or%20army%20officer%20who%20has%20done%20a%20spot%20of%20duty%20in%20a%20conflict%20zone%20and%20they%20will%20have%20a%20litany%20of%20complaints%20and%20suggestions%20on%20how%20the%20media%20should%20do%20its%20job.%20As%20will%20those%20who%20are%20critical%20of%20the%20way%20the%20security%20forces%20operate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20democratisation%20of%20the%20media%20has%20been%20triggered%20exponentially%20by%20revolutionary%20enhancements%20in%20technologies%20of%20information%3B%20there%20is%20a%20virtual%20chaos%2C%20with%20a%20million%20mobile%20handlers%20churning%20out%20distortion%20and%20disparagement.%20There%20are%20no%20standards%3B%20nothing%20is%20considered%20sacred%2C%20nothing%20profane.%20It%20is%20a%20state%20of%20nature%2C%20everyone%20is%20at%20war%20with%20everyone%2C%20to%20paraphrase%20Thomas%20Hobbes.%20And%2C%20when%20ethnic%20groups%20declare%20war%20on%20one%20another%2C%20the%20notions%20of%20media%20objectivity%20and%20professional%20neutrality%20are%20the%20first%20casualty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20months%2C%20Manipur%20has%20tragically%20willed%20itself%20into%20a%20self-feeding%20cycle%20of%20violence.%20The%20agencies%20of%20state%20and%20governance%20in%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Imphal%20have%20overplayed%20the%20hand%20of%20majoritarian%20viciousness.%20The%20media%20in%20Manipur%2C%20too%2C%20succumbed%20to%20this%20game%20of%20ethnic%20antagonism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20an%20extensive%20internal%20conversation%2C%20the%20Guild%20decided%20to%20send%20a%20three-member%20team%20to%20Manipur.%20The%20overwhelming%20majority%20of%20the%20editors%20in%20the%20Guild%20belong%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmainland%E2%80%9D%20and%20none%20has%20any%20fish%20to%20fry%20in%20the%20Manipur%20ethnic%20fires.%C2%A0%20It%20is%20in%20this%20context%20that%20the%20Editors%20Guild%20wages%20a%20lone%2C%20and%20perhaps%20a%20losing%2C%20battle%20to%20remind%20media%20professionals%20of%20norms%20and%20ethics.%20To%20restore%20a%20semblance%20of%20order.%20The%20very%20instrument%20of%20an%20inquiry%20team%20is%20anchored%20in%20the%20journalist%E2%80%99s%20sacred%20obligations%E2%80%94of%20public%20duty%20to%20inform%20and%20educate%20readers%20and%20citizens.%20For%20this%2C%20the%20Guild%20and%20its%20team%20members%20are%20being%20harassed%20and%20prosecuted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Normalising%20the%20Death%20of%20a%20Free%20Press%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fmanipur-media-coverage-normalising-the-death-of-a-free-press%5C%22%3ENormalising%20the%20Death%20of%20a%20Free%20Press%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20kind%20of%20professional%20challenge%20is%20posed%20by%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%E2%80%99s%20totally%20misconceived%20%E2%80%98boycott%E2%80%99%20decision%20against%20some%20TV%20anchors%20and%20news%20channels.%20Opposition%20parties%20feel%20they%20have%20more%20than%20a%20legitimate%20cause%20to%20believe%20that%20some%20sections%20of%20the%20media%2C%20mainly%20electronic%2C%20are%20consistently%20unfair%20to%20them%20and%20that%20these%20offending%20channels%20and%20anchors%20are%20guided%20by%20considerations%20other%20than%20professional%20norms.%20It%20is%20generally%20agreed%20that%20the%20Indian%20media%20seems%20to%20have%20surrendered%20its%20most-cherished%20duty%20to%20%E2%80%9Cspeak%20truth%20to%20power.%E2%80%9D%20Most%20journalists%20have%20lost%20their%20professional%20sure-footedness%20and%20intellectual%20elan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecently%20an%20anchor%2C%20newly%20inducted%20in%20the%20India%20Today%20group%2C%20was%20humiliated%20openly%20by%20a%20Union%20minister%20who%20raked%20up%20the%20controversial%20journalist%E2%80%99s%20criminal%20past%3B%20this%20was%20breath-taking%20audacity.%20None%20of%20the%20other%20senior%20editors%20witness%20to%20this%20intimidation%20had%20the%20moral%20courage%20to%20protest%20the%20minister%E2%80%99s%20outrageous%20bullying.%20Yet%2C%20when%20the%20same%20anchor%20is%20%E2%80%98black-listed%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20INDIA%2C%20his%20fellow-editors%20express%20disapproval%20and%20rightly%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20authoritative%20forum%20of%20appeal%20which%20an%20aggrieved%20citizen%20or%20group%20or%20political%20party%20can%20approach%20with%20a%20complaint%20against%20this%20or%20that%20journalist.%20Many%20of%20these%20are%20even%20beyond%20the%20reach%20of%20%E2%80%9Cname%20and%20shame%E2%80%9D%20ministrations.%20Such%20%E2%80%9Cmedia%20professionals%E2%80%9D%20end%20up%20doing%20grave%20harm%20to%20the%20protocols%20of%20a%20level%20playing%20field.%20This%20has%20terrible%20consequences%20for%20society%20and%20our%20collective%20morals%20and%20manners.%20No%20political%20party%20or%20leader%20can%20coerce%20a%20newspaper%20or%20channel%20to%20be%20fair.%20The%20only%20remedy%20lies%20in%20invocation%20of%20moral%20suasion.%20A%20society%20that%20no%20longer%20subscribes%20to%20some%20minimal%20notions%20of%20fair%20play%20can%20aspire%20neither%20to%20greatness%20nor%20civilisational%20nobility%2C%20notwithstanding%20the%20heralding%20of%20a%20faux%20%3Cem%3EAmrit%20Kaal%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fhkhare%5C%22%3EHarish%20Khare%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20former%20editor-in-chief%20of%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3EThe%20Tribune%3Ci%3E.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694936913000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07112943%2FScreenshot-2023-09-07-at-11.28.4.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fjournalism-in-modis-amrit-kaal-is-risky-business%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20criminal%20case%20against%20the%20Editors%20Guild%20and%20its%20team%20for%20their%20report%20on%20Manipur%20is%20unprecedented.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fjournalism-in-modis-amrit-kaal-is-risky-business%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Soni%20Razdan%20recalls%20thrill%20of%20a%20BEST%20bus%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694936888000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-10372