0was%20handed%20to%20us%20on%20a%20plate%2C%20along%20with%20a%20carefully%20crafted%20Constitution%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EManipur%20was%20followed%20by%20Nuh%20and%20we%20knew%20that%20the%20country%20had%20changed.%20That%20we%20were%20back%20in%20the%201940s%20when%20one%20rumour%2C%20one%20carcass%20discovered%20in%20a%20place%20of%20worship%2C%20one%20quarrel%20over%20kite%20flying%20can%20result%20in%20bloody%20communal%20clashes.%20When%20it%20began%20escalating%2C%20for%20a%20long%20time%20there%20were%20protests%20and%20demonstrations%20to%20prove%20our%20capacity%20to%20fight%20back%20against%20communalism%2C%20sexism%20and%20casteism.%20But%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20realise%20that%20politics%20kept%20pushing%20us%20towards%20relapses%20into%20the%20consolidated%20barbarity%20of%201947.%20That%20was%20when%20the%20historic%20fault%20lines%20were%20thrown%20into%20motion%20after%201857.%20They%20had%20never%20dissolved%20but%20remained%20active%20and%20helped%20sell%20the%20dream%20of%20%E2%80%98Ek%20Bharat%20Akhand%20Bharat%2C%20Ek%20Nishan%2C%20Ek%20Vidhan%E2%80%99!%20Because%20the%20Hindu%20is%20endangered!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20of%20us%20who%20protested%20(specially%20in%20the%20vernaculars)%20when%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20was%20brought%20down%2C%20were%20told%20by%20the%20politicians%20high%20on%20Hindu%20identity%20and%20reunification%20of%20Akhand%20Bharat%2C%20that%20the%20secular%20train%20the%20likes%20of%20us%20relied%20on%20had%20departed%20from%20the%20platform.%20In%202023%2C%20when%2052%20shades%20of%20Hindutva%20are%20in%20the%20air%20and%20every%20chief%20ministerial%20wannabe%20is%20bowing%20at%20this%20temple%20and%20that%2C%20all%20plastered%20with%20sandalwood%20paste%2C%20we%20are%20witnessing%20where%20that%20fabled%20secularism%20terminated.%20The%20high%20ground%20for%20being%20an%20%E2%80%98Asli%20Hindu%E2%80%99%20has%20already%20been%20claimed%20by%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20popular%20slogan%20that%20largely%20unites%20the%20aggressive%20%3Cem%3Etrishul%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%93%20and%20sword-wielding%20lynch%20mobs%20into%20attacking%20minorities%20and%20tribes%20other%20than%20their%20own%20is%20%E2%80%9Cthrow%20out%20all%20foreigners%20(read%20non-Hindus)%20or%20make%20them%20say%20Jai%20Shri%20Ram%20and%20accept%20the%20superiority%20of%20the%20majority%20community%E2%80%9D.%20It%20is%20senseless%20talking%20to%20them%20of%20the%20constitutional%20provisions.%20Justice%20is%20being%20wielded%20by%20mobs%2C%20occasionally%20also%20the%20state%20police%20even%20before%20the%20FIR%20has%20been%20filed.%20It%20seems%20that%20the%20law%20and%20order%20in%20state%20after%20state%20may%20end%20up%20being%20handed%20to%20the%20tender%20mercies%20of%20demolition%20crews%20whose%20loyalty%20is%20with%20the%20Hindu%20nation%20state%2C%20not%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20rage%20cools%2C%20sadness%20and%20anger%20still%20remain.%20What%20dull%20wittedness%20got%20us%20to%20pile%20the%20injustices%20of%20a%20half%20developed%20capitalism%20on%20socialism%20without%20realising%20that%20there%20is%20no%20%E2%80%98trickle%20down%E2%80%99%20of%20wealth%20in%20the%20real%20life%20of%20nations%20and%20the%20romanticised%20loneliness%20of%20the%20fat%20cats%20on%20top%20is%20nothing%20compared%20to%20the%20loneliness%20of%20the%20billions%20crowding%20around%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20power%20pyramid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeetings%20are%20being%20held%20in%20both%20camps%2C%20the%20ruling%20coalition%20and%20the%20Opposition%20INDIA.%20At%20this%20point%20political%20strategy%20making%20needs%20the%20very%20people%20both%20sides%20seem%20intent%20on%20keeping%20out.%20These%20are%20groups%20disliked%20only%20because%20they%20remind%20us%20of%20the%20our%20ancestors%E2%80%99%20own%20exploitative%20expansion%20in%20India%20by%20grabbing%20land%20and%20women%2C%20of%20the%20long%20colonial%20past%20that%20followed%20after%20a%20few%20centuries%20of%20having%20it%20good.%20A%20look%20at%20the%20handbooks%20prepared%20for%20G20%20guests%20shows%20the%20impossibility%20of%20excising%20Bharat%20from%20India%20or%20Hindustan%20even%20though%20dozens%20of%20government%20departments%20may%20have%20tried.%20How%20do%20you%20cover%20up%20the%20Qutub%20Minar%2C%20the%20Taj%20Mahal%3F%20The%20Raisina%20Hill%20buildings%20or%20the%20tomb%20of%20Humayun%20%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWomen%20from%20the%20unorganised%20sector%20are%20the%20first%20group%20kept%20deliberately%20away%20from%20proportionate%20representation%20during%20vital%20debates%20at%20home%20and%20in%20the%20markets%20and%20the%20Parliament.%20They%20are%20followed%20by%20the%20minorities%20and%20tribals.%20Most%20of%20them%20speak%20in%20vernaculars%2C%20not%20the%20smooth%20English%20or%20Sanskritised%20Hindi%20of%20the%20power%20packs%20on%20either%20side.%20They%20are%20kept%20away%20because%20their%20epistemological%20stance%20on%20political%20participation%2C%20on%20economy%20and%20jurisprudence%20is%20very%20different%20from%20the%20mainstream%20and%20will%20pressurise%20the%20system%20into%20effecting%20major%20changes%20in%20power%20distribution.%20To%20justify%20their%20ostracisation%2C%20they%20are%20stigmatised%20as%20being%20under%20educated%2C%20being%20too%20emotionally%20driven%2C%20their%20analysis%20being%20based%20not%20on%20data%20but%20anecdotes.%20If%20at%20all%2C%20they%20are%20included%20in%20cultural%20performances%3A%20promotional%20ads%2C%20documentaries%2C%20theatre%20and%20films%20and%20OTT%20serials.%20There%20they%20are%20cute%20home%20makers%2C%20happy%20wives%20of%20farmers%2C%20gangsters%2C%20whores%2C%20thieves%20and%20dacoits.%20But%20if%20seated%20at%20the%20high%20table%2C%20they%20remind%20silent%20followers%20of%20the%20formally%20laid%20procedures%20rather%20than%20articulate%20free%20minds%20that%20may%20choose%20to%20speak%20on%20the%20injustices%20of%20a%20monolithic%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInclusion%20is%20what%20we%20need%20now.%20When%20the%20body%20of%20one%20of%20our%20greatest%20vocalists%2C%20Kumar%20Gandharva%2C%20was%20carried%20to%20the%20cremation%20grounds%20in%20his%20home%20town%20Devas%2C%20his%20pall%20bearers%20were%20led%20by%20a%20band%20of%20a%20wandering%20Nirguniya%20singers.%20Their%20sect%20pays%20homage%20in%20folk%20songs%20to%20a%20great%20abstract%20god%2C%20who%20stands%20above%20all%20caste%20or%20creed.%20Perhaps%20Kumar%20ji%20had%20willed%20that%20it%20be%20so.%20He%20had%20reintegrated%20their%20songs%20in%20his%20own%20classical%20repertoire%20so%20he%20wished%20to%20be%20accompanied%20by%20the%20deeply%20philosophical%2C%20despairingly%20gay%20and%20ironical%20Nirgun%20music%20till%20the%20end%20%2Cas%20his%20mortal%20remains%20turned%20slowly%20to%20ashes%20and%20dust.%20If%20the%20Nirgun%20songs%20reminding%20us%20of%20the%20irrelevance%20of%20borders%2C%20of%20our%20mortality%20and%20the%20eventual%20disappearance%20into%20the%20elements%2C%20were%20to%20penetrate%20their%20minds%2C%20a%20sensitive%20leadership%20would%20be%20mortified%20at%20the%20very%20thought%20of%20abrogating%20to%20oneself%20the%20rather%20ridiculous%20task%20of%20planning%20for%20a%20thousand%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMrinal%20Pande%20is%20a%20writer%20and%20veteran%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694934015000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F17123146%2Fsrivatsan-balaji-T5s48osIQTU-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fwho-is-afraid-of-otherness%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20seems%20that%20the%20law%20and%20order%20in%20state%20after%20state%20may%20end%20up%20being%20handed%20to%20the%20tender%20mercies%20of%20demolition%20crews%20whose%20loyalty%20is%20with%20the%20Hindu%20nation%20state%2C%20not%20the%20Constitution.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fwho-is-afraid-of-otherness%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%