e%20are%20speculations%20that%20Ali%20might%20direct%20the%20project.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fwill-shahid-kapoor-and-kareena-kapoor-reunite-for-jab-we-met-sequel-heres-what-we-know-%2Farticleshow%2F103727440.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Libya%3A%20Aid%20Groups%20Demand%20More%20Help%20After%20Devastating%20Floods%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F17104809%2FF6FsVciWkAAjmld.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Flibya-flood-civil-society-unites-in-ramping-up-aid%2Fa-66809638%5C%22%3EAid%20groups%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20Saturday%20called%20for%20increased%20global%20support%20in%20the%20wake%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Flibya-thousands-feared-dead-after-storm-daniel%2Fa-66783443%5C%22%3Edevastating%20floods%20in%20eastern%20Libya%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20humanitarian%20situation%20in%20Libya%20is%20nothing%20short%20of%20catastrophic%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0said%20Bashir%20Omar%2C%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20International%20Committee%20of%20the%20Red%20Cross%20(ICRC)%20in%20Libya.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20needs%20far%20exceed%20the%20capabilities%20of%20all%20international%20organizations%20operating%20in%20Libya%20and%20the%20local%20authorities.%20Consequently%2C%20international%20support%20is%20imperative%20to%20overcome%20this%20catastrophe%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20international%20aid%20shipments%20began%20to%20arrive%20in%20Libya%20on%20Saturday%2C%20providing%20a%20lifeline%20to%20thousands%20of%20survivors.%C2%A0The%20World%20Health%20Organization%20said%C2%A029%20tonnes%20of%20aid%20had%20arrived%20in%20the%20eastern%20city%20of%20Benghazi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWater-borne%20diseases%20could%20spread%20easily%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERescue%20groups%20also%20said%20the%20possibility%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Flibya-flood-search-continues-for-more-than-10000-missing%2Fa-66820356%5C%22%3Efinding%20survivors%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0seemed%20bleak%2C%20as%20they%C2%A0warned%20that%20the%20spread%20of%20disease%20could%20exacerbate%20the%20humanitarian%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20looming%20concern%20is%20the%20potential%20outbreak%20of%20cholera%2C%20which%20could%20pose%20a%20significant%20threat%20to%20survivors.%20Reports%20have%20already%20emerged%20of%20several%20children%20falling%20ill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Health%20Ministry%20of%20the%20Tripoli-based%20government%20of%20Libya%20has%20indicated%20that%20the%20rapid%20spread%20of%20this%20deadly%20bacteria%20is%20a%20significant%20risk%20due%20to%20groundwater%20contamination%20resulting%20from%20the%20presence%20of%20corpses%2C%20decaying%20animal%20carcasses%2C%20waste%2C%20and%20chemicals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20strongly%20advise%20people%20to%20avoid%20approaching%20the%20wells%20in%20Derna%2C%E2%80%9D%20cautioned%20Libyan%20Health%20Minister%20Ibrahim%20Al-Arabi%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20city%20most%20severely%20impacted%20by%20the%20storm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThousands%20of%20people%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20anywhere%20to%20sleep%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20food%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Salah%20Aboulgasem%2C%20the%20deputy%20director%20of%20partner%20development%20from%20the%20Islamic%20Relief%20organization.%20In%20conditions%20like%20this%2C%20diseases%20can%20quickly%20spread%20as%20water%20systems%20are%20contaminated.%20The%20city%20smells%20like%20death.%20Almost%20everyone%20has%20lost%20someone%20they%20know.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUN%20Emergency%20Relief%20Coordinator%20Martin%20Griffiths%20stressed%20that%20the%20top%20priorities%20for%20Libya%20are%20%E2%80%9Cshelter%2C%20food%2C%20key%20primary%20medical%20care%20because%20of%20the%20worry%20of%20cholera%2C%20particularly%20in%20Libya%20the%20worry%20of%20lack%20of%20clean%20water.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFloods%20caused%20two%20dams%20to%20collapse%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20floods%20were%20caused%20by%20a%20powerful%20storm%2C%20which%C2%A0overwhelmed%C2%A0two%20dams%2C%20sending%20a%20wall%20of%20water%20several%20meters%20(yards)%20high%20through%C2%A0the%20eastern%20city%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fderna-the-libyan-city-known-for-rebellion-and-neglect%2Fa-66822261%5C%22%3EDerna%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20destroying%20entire%20neighborhoods%20and%20sweeping%20people%20out%20to%20sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%2020%2C000%20people%20are%20feared%20dead%20and%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20are%20missing%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Libyan%20Red%20Crescent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVarying%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Flibya-flood-global-aid-effort-intensifies-as-death-toll-rises%2Fa-66807395%5C%22%3Edeath%20toll%20figures%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0have%20emerged%20from%20different%20sources%2C%20ranging%20from%205%2C000%20to%2011%2C000.%20The%20World%20Health%20Organization%20said%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20bodies%20of%203%2C958%20people%20have%20been%20recovered%20and%20identified%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0while%C2%A0the%20official%20death%20toll%20rose%C2%A0to%203%2C166.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELibyan%20National%20Army%20(LNA)%20spokesman%20Major%20General%20Ahmed%C2%A0al-Mismari%20said%20900%2C000%20people%20lived%20in%20the%20affected%20areas.%20He%20said%20the%20floods%20washed%20away%20all%20roads%20and%20bridges%C2%A0and%20have%20made%20it%20difficult%20to%20travel%20from%20one%20area%20to%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20ICRC%20dispatched%20a%20plane%20carrying%205%2C000%20body%20bags%20from%20Geneva%20to%20Benghazi%20in%20eastern%20Libya.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20Libya%E2%80%99s%C2%A0Public%20Prosecutor%20Al-Siddiq%20Al-Sour%20said%20he%20would%20ensure%20justice%20for%C2%A0those%20responsible%20for%20the%20Derna%20Dam%20disaster.%20An%20investigation%20has%20been%20opened%20into%20what%20caused%20the%20collapse%20of%20the%20Wadi%20Derna%20dam%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELibya%20is%20in%20a%20politically%20unstable%20situation%20as%20two%20rival%20governments%20strive%20for%20control.%20The%20country%20has%20been%20mired%20in%20chaos%20since%20the%20overthrow%20of%20dictator%20Moammar%20Gadhafi%C2%A0in%202011%2C%20with%20one%20government%20based%20in%20the%20east%20and%20another%20in%20the%20capital%2C%20Tripoli.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20concerns%20have%20been%20raised%20about%20the%20presence%20of%20unexploded%20ordnance%20and%20abandoned%20munition%20stores%20in%20Derna%2C%20posing%20an%20%E2%80%9Cadditional%20challenge%E2%80%9D%20to%20residents%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Red%20Cross.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20collapse%20of%20the%20dams%20has%20sparked%20allegations%20of%20neglect%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20maintenance%20over%20the%20years.%20Following%20the%20disaster%2C%20online%20warnings%20surfaced%20about%20a%20third%20dam%20east%20of%20Benghazi%20being%20at%20risk%20of%20collapsing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20east-based%20government%20reassured%20the%20public%20that%20the%20al-Qatra%20and%20Wadi%20Jaza%20dams%20were%20under%20control.%20Water%20and%20sanitation%20officials%20inspected%20both%20facilities%20and%20initiated%20efforts%20to%20install%20new%20pumps%20to%20alleviate%20pressure%20on%20Wadi%20Jaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Flibya-aid-groups-demand-more-help-after-devastating-floods%2Fa-66830912%5C%22%3Eoriginally%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20DW.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694927932000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F17104809%2FF6FsVciWkAAjmld.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Flibya-aid-groups-demand-more-help-after-devastating