76%20years%20of%20independence%2C%20this%20attitude%20of%20respect%20and%20reverence%20has%20not%20only%20deteriorated%2C%20but%20poisoned%20the%20younger%20generation%20of%20students%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20recent%20incident%20in%20Nanguneri%20%E2%80%93%20where%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftamil-nadu%2Ffelled-by-caste-pride-in-tamil-nadus-nanguneri-town%2Farticle67235233.ece%5C%22%3Ea%20group%20of%20dominant%20Marvar%20caste%20students%20attacked%20their%20classmate%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20belonged%20to%20a%20Scheduled%20Caste%2C%20with%20a%20sickle%2C%20causing%20life%20threatening%20injuries%20%E2%80%93%20has%20once%20again%20revealed%20the%20venomous%20casteism%20in%20the%20land%20of%20social%20justice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20victim%2C%20Chinnadurai%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eone%20of%20the%20diligent%20students%20in%20his%20class%2C%20had%20been%20getting%20harassed%20by%20his%20classmates%20who%20belonged%20to%20the%20dominant%20caste.%20He%20was%20attacked%20the%20same%20night%20his%20mother%20had%20finally%20complained%20to%20the%20principal.%20The%20boy%E2%80%99s%20sister%20was%20also%20injured%20and%20his%20grandfather%20died%20while%20staging%20a%20protest%20after%20the%20attack.%20Chinnadurai%20and%20his%20sister%20are%20under%20treatment%20in%20hospital.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20fact%20finding%20report%20of%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Union%20for%20Civil%20Liberties%20(PUCL)%20and%20Dalit%20Intellectual%20Collective%20(DIC)%20has%20revealed%20the%20entrenched%20casteism%20in%20Nanguneri%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EPeople%20from%20the%20dominant%20caste%2C%20being%20landholders%20in%20this%20region%2C%20have%20made%20people%20from%20the%20Dalit%20community%20either%20move%20to%20other%20cities%20for%20employment%20or%20forced%20them%20to%20become%20subservient%20to%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAny%20attempts%20by%20Dalits%20to%20become%20self-employed%2C%20like%20by%20driving%20an%20auto%20rickshaw%2C%20are%20discouraged%20by%20the%20dominant%20caste.%20Even%20access%20to%20the%20public%20distribution%20system%20was%20made%20difficult%20for%20the%20community%2C%20according%20to%20the%20PUCL%20report.%20However%2C%20after%20this%20violent%20incident%20it%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Esurreptitiously%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Erestored%20to%20their%20locality%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20assembly%20speaker%20and%20collector%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20usury%20by%20dominant%20caste%20members%20at%20exorbitant%20interest%20rates%20has%20forced%20many%20Dalits%20to%20lose%20their%20land%20to%20them%20as%20they%20failed%20to%20pay%20the%20money%20back.%20DIC%E2%80%99s%20extensive%20report%20highlighted%20the%20prevalent%20glorification%20of%20caste%20indicative%20images%20and%20symbols%20in%20public%20places%20and%20institutions%20that%20explicitly%20polarise%20people%20based%20on%20their%20caste.%20This%20hostile%20environment%2C%20coupled%20with%20violence%2C%20has%20caused%20the%20landholding%20of%20Dalits%20to%20reduce%20considerably%20as%20many%20have%20migrated%20out%20of%20Nanguneri.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20violent%20caste%20consciousness%20among%20the%20school%20children%20reflects%20the%20prevailing%20%E2%80%9Chabitus%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20was%20defined%20by%20French%20sociologist%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EPierre%20Bourdieu%20as%20people%E2%80%99s%20embodied%20traits%20and%20behaviours%20which%20are%20learned%20through%20socialisation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20cultural%20traits%20are%20so%20ingrained%20with%20such%20caste-based%20differentiation%20that%20our%20behaviour%20and%20attitude%20reeks%20of%20casteism%20in%20the%20public%20sphere.%20And%20by%20extension%2C%20existing%20social%20inequality%2C%20violence%20and%20discrimination%20are%20considered%20natural%20without%20any%20compunction.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20in%20the%20private%20sphere%2C%20caste%20consciousness%20is%20so%20strong%20that%20according%20to%20the%20third%20National%20Family%20Health%20Survey%20(NFHS-3)%2C%20only%202.59%25%20of%20marriages%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20were%20inter-caste%2C%20which%20is%20very%20low%20compared%20to%20many%20other%20states.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EFurther%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20NFHS-5%20conducted%20between%202019-2021%20showed%20that%20the%20state%20has%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20consanguineous%20marriages%20at%2028%25%20compared%20to%20national%20average%20of%2011%25.%20In%20consanguineous%20marriages%2C%20the%20husband%20and%20wife%20are%20related%20by%20blood%2C%20belonging%20to%20the%20same%20community.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20shocking%20to%20see%20such%20caste%20consciousness%20even%20among%20politicians%20from%20Dravidian%20political%20parties%20(Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(DMK)%20and%20All%20India%20Anna%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(AIDMK))%20that%20were%20formed%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20social%20justice%20and%20elimination%20of%20caste-based%20discrimination.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%201997%2C%20six%20Dalits%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftamil-nadu%2Fremembering-melavalavu-massacre%2Farticle65585014.ece%5C%22%3Etwo%20Dalit%20leaders%20of%20Melavaluvu%20panchayat%2C%20were%20hacked%20to%20death%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20daylight%2C%20near%20Madurai%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20Seventeen%20people%20were%20sentenced%20to%20life%20in%202001.%20But%20three%20men%20were%20released%20on%20remission%20by%20the%20DMK%20during%20the%20Anna%20birth%20centenary%20celebrations%20in%202008%20and%20the%20remaining%2013%20(one%20died)%20were%20released%20by%20AIADMK%20in%202019%20during%20MGR%20birth%20celebrations%20for%20their%20%E2%80%98good%E2%80%99%20conduct.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202020%2C%20DMK%20organising%20secretary%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20R.S.%20Bharathi%20made%20a%20controversial%20comment%20when%20he%20called%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftamil-nadu%2Frs-bharathi-moves-hc-in-scst-atrocities-case%2Farticle31643923.ece%5C%22%3Eelevation%20of%20judges%20belonging%20to%20scheduled%20caste%20communities%20%E2%80%9Calms%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20provided%20by%20former%20chief%20minister%20M.%20Karunanidhi.%20While%20he%20was%20briefly%20arrested%2C%20DMK%20failed%20to%20as%20much%20as%20condemn%20his%20anti-Dalit%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20same%20year%2C%20DMK%20MPs%20Dayanidhi%20Maran%20and%20TR%20Baalu%2C%20while%20being%20denied%20permission%20to%20meet%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20chief%20secretary%20shouted%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAre%20we%20Dalits%20to%20be%20treated%20like%20this%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Ftamil-nadu%2Fone-meeting-many-controversies-row-over-dmk-mps-meeting-tn-chief-secy-124649%5C%22%3EFearing%20arrest%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20the%20SC%2FST%20Act%2C%20both%20of%20them%20sought%20anticipatory%20bail%20immediately.%20The%20non-Dalits%20and%20non-Brahmins%20being%20the%20backbone%20of%20Dravidian%20parties%2C%20we%20find%20such%20casteist%2C%20hate-filled%20statements%20from%20both%20AIADMK%20and%20DMK%20leaders%20regularly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20March%202022%2C%20DMK%20minister%20R.S.%20Rajakanappan%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fdmk-transport-minister-sacked-caste-slur-allegation-government-official-1931113-2022-03-29%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewas%20shifted%20from%20the%20transport%20ministry%20and%20handed%20the%20backward%20classes%20welfare%20portfolio%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20after%20harassing%20a%20block%20development%20officer%20who%20belonged%20to%20the%20Dalit%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuch%20embodied%20traits%20give%20confidence%20and%20institutional%20support%20for%20indulging%20in%20violent%20crimes%20against%20Dalits%2C%20as%20we%20witnessed%20in%20the%20Nanguneri%20incident.%20The%20National%20Crimes%20Record%20Bureau%20(NCRB)%20data%20shows%20increasing%20violence%20against%20Dalits%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBetween%202019%20and%202021%2C%20reported%20cases%20of%20such%20violence%20in%20the%20state%20increased%20by%20nearly%2020%25%2C%20compared%20to%20the%20national%20average%20of%209.7%25.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EViduthalai%20Chiruthaigal%20Katchi%20(VCK)%20and%20communist%20parties%20have%20been%20demanding%20a%20law%20against%20honour%20killings%20without%20success%2C%20as%20it%20might%20dent%20the%20party%20in%20power%E2%80%99s%20dominant%20caste%20vote%20bank.%20The%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20or%20CPI(M)%20MLA%20M.%20Chinnadurai%E2%80%99s%20demand%20for%20the%20release%20of%20a%20white%20paper%20by%20the%20government%20on%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20Sub%20Plan%20(SCSP)%20and%20Tribal%20Sub%20Plan%20(TSP)%20expenditure%20shows%20the%20lack%20of%20transparency%20in%20government%20spending%20on%20SC%2FST%20communities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20landlessness%20among%20the%20Dalits%20in%20Nanguneri%20is%20not%20an%20isolated%20incident%20as%20Dalits%20hold%20only%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E7.8%25%20of%20farmlands%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20according%20to%20Tamil%20Nadu%20State%20Agricultural%20Department%E2%80%99s%20report%2C%20%E2%80%98Salient%20Statistics%20on%20Agriculture%20%2C%202019%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Panchami%20land%2C%20which%20was%20distributed%20to%20Dalits%20by%20the%20British%20government%2C%20is%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20dominant%20caste%20and%20DMK%2C%20which%20promised%20its%20recovery%20in%20its%202016%20election%20manifesto%2C%20has%20conveniently%20skipped%20it%20in%20the%202021%20version.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDMK%20constituted%20a%20committee%20headed%20by%20former%20Madras%20high%20court%20judge%20Maruthamuthu%20in%202011%20to%20examine%20issues%20related%20to%20Panchami%20lands.%20This%20committee%20was%20dissolved%20when%20AIADMK%20came%20to%20power.%20According%20to%20the%20DIC%20report%2C%20very%20few%20Dalits%20in%20Nanguneri%20are%20in%20government%20employment%20and%20a%20majority%20of%20them%20work%20as%20labourers.%20In%202000%2C%20a%20white%20paper%20titled%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EReservation%20in%20Government%20Employment%20for%20the%20Adi-Dravidars%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20Backward%20Classes%2C%20Most%20Backward%20Classes%20and%20De-Notified%20Communities%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20was%20released%20by%20then%20chief%20minister%20Karunanidhi%2C%20which%20showed%20that%20SC%2FST%20and%20Most%20Backward%20Classes%E2%80%99%20(MBC)%20representation%20in%20government%20jobs%20was%20way%20below%20the%20constitutionally%20mandated%20percentage.%20The%20All%20India%20Survey%20on%20Higher%20Education%20(AISHE)%202020-21%20also%20reaffirmed%20the%20underrepresentation%20of%20Dalits%20in%20government%20and%20private%20sector%20without%20any%20change%20from%20the%20year%202000.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETrying%20to%20bring%20in%20superfluous%20changes%20at%20the%20school%20level%20cannot%20be%20a%20solution%20to%20this%20caste-filled%20habitus%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20The%20Dravidian%20political%20ideology%20needs%20to%20relook%20and%20reorient%20itself%20in%20bringing%20about%20transformation%20at%20every%20level%2C%20including%20its%20own%20party%20structure%20and%20its%20leaders.%20There%20is%20an%20urgent%20need%20to%20critically%20evaluate%20political%20parties%E2%80%99%20caste-based%20candidate%20selection%20and%20vote%20bank%20politics.%20Such%20incidents%20are%20bound%20to%20repeat%20if%20there%20are%20no%20structural%20changes%20to%20how%20caste%20is%20perceived%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EVenkatanarayanan%20S.%20is%20an%20associate%20professor%20and%20head%20of%20the%20of%20Political%20Science%20and%20History%20department%20at%20Christ%20University%2C%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694927679000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2F27162618%2FIMG_2018.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fthere-is-an-urgent-need-to-address-how-caste-is-perceived-in-tamil-nadu%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Our%20cultural%20traits%20are%20so%20ingrained%20with%20caste-based%20differentiation%20that%20our%20behaviour%20and%20attitude%20reeks%20of%20casteism%20in%20the%20public%20sphere.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fthere-is-an-urgent-need-to-address-how-caste-is-perceived-in-tamil-nadu%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Plane%20crash%20in%20Amazon%20rainforest%20kills%2014%20tourists%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694927160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F09%2F768x432%2Fskynews-brazil-barcelos-amazonas_6287924.jpg%3F20230917062610%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fbrazil-plane-crash-14-dead-after-aircraft-carrying-tourists-crashes-in-amazon-rainforest-12963261%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Fourteen%20people%20have%20died%20in%20a%20plane%20crash%20in%20the%20Amazon%20rainforest%2C%20according%20to%20officials.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fbrazil-plane-crash-14-dead-after-aircraft-carrying-tourists-crashes-in-amazon-rainforest-12963261%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews