the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcong-appoints-new-working-committee-ahead-of-elections%5C%22%3Enew%20CWC%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20includes%2039%20main%20members%2C%20who%20were%20appointed%20by%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20in%20August.%20It%20also%20has%20special%20invitees%2C%20ex-officio%20members%20and%20incharges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20day%20one%20of%20the%20meeting%2C%20the%20party%20passed%20a%20main%20resolution%20as%20well%20as%20three%20separate%20ones.%20This%20included%20a%20condolence%20resolution%20on%20the%20demise%20of%20former%20Kerala%20chief%20minister%20Oomen%20Chandy%2C%20a%20resolution%20on%20the%20ongoing%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20Manipur%2C%20as%20well%20as%20one%20committing%20to%20rebuild%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20where%20over%20400%20people%20have%20died%20after%20unprecedented%20rain%20and%20floods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%2C%20which%20comes%20ahead%20of%20the%20general%20elections%20next%20year%20and%20five%20state%20elections%20this%20year%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana%2C%20will%20continue%20on%20Sunday%20when%20the%20party%20is%20expected%20to%20take%20up%20organisational%20issues%20around%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20will%20speak%20in%20detail%20on%20the%20organisational%20issues%20surrounding%20the%20upcoming%20Legislative%20Assembly%20and%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20tomorrow%20in%20the%20Extended%20CWC%20Meeting%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Kharge%20in%20his%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20meeting%2C%20addressing%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20Saturday%20morning%2C%20Congress%20spokesperson%20and%20media%20and%20publicity%20department%20chief%20Pawan%20Khera%20said%20that%20discussions%20would%20be%20held%20in%20a%20free%20and%20fair%20manner%20while%20hailing%20the%20%E2%80%9Chistoric%E2%80%9D%20election%20of%20Kharge%20as%20the%20party%20chief%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20Kharge%E2%80%99s%20election%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Chistoric%E2%80%9D%20milestone%20for%20the%20party%2C%20Khera%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CNo%20other%20party%20in%20this%20country%20has%20had%20this%20kind%20of%20an%20open%20election.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20very%20proud%20of%20our%20tradition%20of%20electing%20our%20president%20through%20an%20open%20election.%20When%20we%20meet%20today%20in%20a%20few%20hours%20from%20now%20in%20the%20CWC%2C%20there%20will%20be%20an%20open%20discussion.%20Everybody%E2%80%99s%20free%20to%20voice%20his%20or%20her%20opinion%2C%20suggestion%2C%20or%20criticism.%20That%20is%20the%20way%20our%20party%20functions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaste%20Census%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20main%20resolution%2C%20the%20CWC%20has%20called%20for%20increasing%20the%20existing%20upper%20limit%20on%20reservations%20for%20SC%2FST%20and%20OBCs%20in%20the%20country%20while%20expressing%20%E2%80%9Cgrave%20concern%E2%80%9D%20for%20increasing%20unemployment%20and%20continuous%20rise%20in%20prices%20of%20essential%20commodities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20CWC%20expresses%20its%20grave%20concern%20at%C2%A0%20increasing%20unemployment%20and%20continuous%20rise%20in%20prices%2C%20especially%C2%A0%20of%20essential%20commodities.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20so-called%20Rozgar%20Melas%20are%20a%20hoax%20to%20cover%20up%20the%20abject%20failure%20to%20create%2C%20as%20promised%2C%20two%20crore%20jobs%20a%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20resolution%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20the%20failure%20to%20conduct%20a%20population%20census%2C%20which%20was%20last%20conducted%20in%202011%2C%20%E2%80%9Cis%C2%A0%20a%20national%20and%20an%20international%20shame.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20consequences%20is%20that%20an%20estimated%2014%20crore%20of%20the%20poorest%20Indians%20are%20denied%20their%20entitlement%20to%20food%20rations%20since%20ration%20cards%20are%20issued%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%202011%20Census.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20CWC%20also%20underlines%20the%20stubborn%20refusal%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20conduct%20a%20Caste%20Census.%20This%C2%A0%20refusal%20in%20the%20face%20of%20a%20universal%20demand%20has%20exposed%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20lack%20of%20commitment%20to%20social%20and%20economic%20justice%20and%20its%20bias%20against%20the%20backward%20classes%2C%20Dalits%20and%20tribal%20people.%20In%20this%20context%2C%20the%20CWC%20also%20calls%20for%20increasing%20the%20existing%20upper%20limit%20of%20reservations%20for%20scheduled%20castes%2C%20scheduled%20tribes%20and%20OBCs%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20conduct%20a%20caste%20census%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20if%20voted%20to%20power.%20It%20has%20also%20urged%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20implement%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-caste-census-ideological-unity-opposition%5C%22%3Ecaste%20census%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CWC%20resolution%20also%20said%20that%20prime%20minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20failed%20in%20his%20promise%20made%20in%20his%20first%20Independence%20Day%20speech%20in%202014%20where%20he%20called%20for%20a%2010-year%20moratorium%20on%20casteism%2C%20communalism%20and%20regionalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIronically%2C%20the%20three%20evils%20have%20aggravated%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20thanks%20to%20the%20divisive%20and%20discriminatory%20policies%20adopted%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20his%20government%20and%20his%20party.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20resolution%20has%20also%20drawn%20attention%20to%20the%20economy%20and%20said%20while%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20economic%20outlook%20remains%20bleak%2C%20the%20government%20is%20solely%20concerned%20with%20%E2%80%9Cheadline%20management%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJPC%20on%20Adani%2C%20call%20for%20a%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20special%20session%20of%20parliament%20due%20to%20begin%20on%20Monday%20(September%2018)%2C%20the%20CWC%20resolution%20has%20reiterated%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20demand%20for%20a%20Joint%20Parliamentary%20Committee%20probe%20into%20the%20allegations%20of%20market%20manipulation%20by%20firms%20linked%20to%20Gautam%20Adani.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20also%20demanded%20that%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%20be%20passed%20during%20the%20special%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20Election%20Commissioners%20Bill%20that%20has%20been%20listed%20for%20consideration%20and%20passage%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%20in%20its%20agenda%20for%20the%20session%20released%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Congress%20said%20that%20the%20legislation%20will%20%E2%80%9Cseverely%20compromise%20the%20independence%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20to%20conduct%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20Saturday%20evening%2C%20while%20deliberations%20on%20the%20final%20resolution%20were%20still%20underway%2C%20former%20union%20minister%20P.%20Chidambaram%20said%20that%20the%20party%20will%20oppose%20the%20bill%20in%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20resolution%20has%20also%20asked%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccome%20clean%20on%20the%20border%20dispute%20with%20China%20and%20take%20a%20resolute%20stand%20against%20any%20challenge%20to%20the%20territorial%20integrity%20of%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20hailed%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20conducted%20by%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20last%20year%20and%20called%20it%20%E2%80%9Ca%20transformational%C2%A0%20moment%20in%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20politics%E2%80%9D%20to%20unite%20the%20people%20against%20the%20forces%20that%20are%20dividing%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20another%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%2C%20Chidambaram%20said%20that%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20second%20instalment%20is%20being%20explored.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20have%20been%20requests%20by%20members%20of%20the%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20(CWC)%20that%20we%20should%20have%20a%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%202%20from%20the%20east%20to%20the%20west.%20That%20matter%20is%20under%20consideration%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Gandhi%20visited%20Ladakh%20in%20a%20five-day%20trip%20to%20the%20union%20territory%20that%20was%20described%20by%20the%20party%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9Coffshoot%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Yatra.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694926505000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F17102313%2FScreenshot-2023-09-17-at-10.20.58-AM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-calls-for-increasing-upper-limit-on-reservations-at-historic-cwc-meeting%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20two-day%20meeting%20is%20the%20first%20conducted%20by%20the%20new%20CWC%20ahead%20of%20general%20elections%20next%20year%20and%20five-state%20elections%20this%20year%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-calls-for-increasing-upper-limit-on-reservations-at-historic-cwc-meeting%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2210%20inches%20of%20downpour%3A%20Torrential%20rain%20torments%20Indore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694925944000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103726852%2Cimgsize-77154.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Findore%2Ftorrential-rain-torments-indore%2Farticleshow%2F103726829.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Continuous%20incessant%20rainfall%20on%20Saturday%20threw%20life%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20commercial%20capital%20completely%20out%20of%20gear.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TNN%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22c