0distinctly%20Hitchcockian%20visual%20of%20a%20murder%20of%20crows%20%E2%80%93%20after%20which%20a%20visibly%20traumatised%20Poirot%20wakes%20up%20in%20his%20apartment%20in%20Venice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20inspired%20choice%20that%20reveals%20Branagh%E2%80%99s%20plans%20to%20move%20away%20from%20glamour%20of%20his%20earlier%20films%20is%20the%20presence%20of%20composer%20Hildur%20Gu%C3%B0nad%C3%B3ttir%20%E2%80%93%20best%20known%20for%20%3Cem%3EJoker%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EChernobyl%3C%2Fem%3E%20(both%20released%20in%202019).%20Gu%C3%B0nad%C3%B3ttir%20%E2%80%93%20famous%20for%20her%20unconventional%20scores%20that%20convey%20mood%20rather%20than%20leaving%20the%20audience%20with%20%E2%80%98melodic%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98hummable%E2%80%99%20pieces%20%E2%80%93%20is%20an%20excellent%20choice%20to%20communicate%20the%20sense%20that%20something%E2%80%99s%20not%20quite%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpening%20in%201947%20in%20the%20city%20of%20canals%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20shown%20Poirot%20in%20self-imposed%20retirement.%20He%20has%20a%20bodyguard%20(Riccardo%20Scarmaccio)%20who%20ensures%20the%20detective%20can%20enjoy%20being%20retired%2C%20without%20being%20hounded%20by%20potential%20clients%20who%20queue%20up%20in%20front%20of%20his%20house%20every%20other%20day.%20He%E2%80%99s%20visited%20by%20a%20friend%20%E2%80%93%20a%20mystery%20writer%20called%20Ariadne%20Oliver%20(Tina%20Fey)%20%E2%80%93%20who%20as%20Poirot%20puts%20it%2C%20is%20there%20to%20seduce%20him%20with%20a%20case%20by%20provoking%20his%20curiosity.%20Oliver%20tells%20Poirot%20about%20a%20psychic%20named%20Joyce%20Reynolds%20(Michelle%20Yeoh)%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20only%20recently%20released%20from%20prison%20%E2%80%93%20claiming%20to%20be%20a%20medium%20who%20talks%20to%20people%20who%20have%20passed%20on.%20As%20a%20mystery%20writer%2C%20Oliver%20tells%20Poirot%20how%20she%E2%80%99s%20uncovered%20nearly%20all%20the%20fraudulent%20ways%20of%20Reynolds%E2%80%99%20kind%2C%20except%20for%20Reynolds%20herself.%20Oliver%20convinces%20Poirot%20to%20participate%20in%20a%20seance%20on%20Halloween%20night%20to%20uncover%20Reynolds%E2%80%99%20tricks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20Christie%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EHallowe%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Een%20Party%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20fine%20set-up.%20What%20better%20way%20to%20start%20off%20a%20story%20about%20(probable)%20spirits%20and%20ghosts%20than%20to%20have%20one%20of%20the%20most%20staunch%20rationalists%20in%20the%20room%3F%20Branagh%20treats%20%3Cem%3EA%20Haunting%20in%20Venice%3C%2Fem%3E%20like%20a%20horror%20film.%20There%20are%20carefully%20crafted%20scares%20that%20are%20almost%20guaranteed%20to%20provoke%20a%20few%20screams%20in%20the%20theatre.%20Reynolds%E2%80%99%20character%20is%20introduced%20wearing%20a%20Noh%20mask%20%E2%80%93%20which%20goes%20on%20to%20become%20an%20important%20plot-point%20in%20the%20film.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20Poirot%20%E2%80%93%20whose%20disdain%20for%20the%20likes%20of%20Reynolds%20cannot%20be%20contained%20%E2%80%93%20is%20confronted%20by%20the%20psychic%20about%20knowing%20the%20curse%20of%20being%20the%20%E2%80%9Cgifted%E2%80%9D%20one.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20tremendous%20moment%20between%20towerings%20actors%20%E2%80%93%20Branagh%20and%20Yeoh%20%E2%80%93%20where%20the%20film%20hints%20that%20everything%20can%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20reasonable%20explanation.%20It%E2%80%99s%20one%20of%20the%20finest%20attributes%20of%20the%20film%20%E2%80%93%20which%20merely%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20go%20about%20debunking%20the%20myths%20like%20a%20checklist%20%E2%80%93%20but%20also%20acknowledges%20that%20even%20the%20wisest%20among%20us%20can%E2%80%99t%20categorically%20explain%20every%20occurrence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20whodunit%20skeleton%20has%20gotten%20a%20reinvention%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20most%20famously%20in%20Rian%20Johnson%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EKnives%20Out%3C%2Fem%3E%20films.%20Johnson%E2%80%99s%20films%20almost%20feel%20like%20feature-length%20winks%20at%20audiences%2C%20given%20how%20the%20films%20use%20the%20tropes%20of%20the%20genre%2C%20suffuse%20them%20with%20%E2%80%98topicality%E2%80%99%20and%20place%20dramatic%20actors%20(to%20varying%20degrees)%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20most%20bizarre%20set-ups.%20And%20his%20films%20are%20undeniably%20sexy%20%E2%80%93%20with%20superb%20performances%2C%20and%20dazzling%20visual%20language%20%E2%80%93%20which%20could%20easily%20spawn%20replicas.%20Thankfully%2C%20Branagh%20goes%20in%20the%20opposite%20direction%20and%20treats%20his%20whodunit%20like%20a%20genre%20film%20rather%20than%20as%20a%20blockbuster.%20The%20result%20is%2C%20the%20visual%20language%20of%20a%20moody%20A24%20film%20(the%20studio%20behind%20the%20excellent%20%3Cem%3ETalk%20To%20Me%20%3C%2Fem%3Erecently)%2C%20rather%20than%20a%20standard%2020th%20Century%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20gothic%20medieval%20architecture%2C%20Gu%C3%B0nad%C3%B3ttir%E2%80%99s%20foreboding%20score%2C%20Branagh%E2%80%99s%20most%20low-key%20ensemble%20%E2%80%93%20including%20Jamie%20Dornan%2C%20Kelly%20Reilly%2C%20Camille%20Cottin%2C%20Kyle%20Allen%2C%20apart%20from%20Fey%20and%20Yeoh%20%E2%80%93%20adds%20up%20to%20a%20mystery%20that%20ties%20up%20its%20loose%20ends%20neatly%2C%20perhaps%20too%20neatly%2C%20by%20the%20end%2C%20but%20one%20that%20also%20references%20old-school%20satisfaction%20of%20mysteries.%20Branagh%E2%80%99s%20ostentatious%20Belgian%20accent%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20get%20in%20the%20way%20of%20a%20haunted%20performance%20of%20a%20man%20%E2%80%93%20who%20knows%20everything%20there%20is%20to%20know%20%E2%80%93%20and%20yet%20seems%20to%20be%20grappling%20with%20the%20unknowables.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBranagh%E2%80%99s%20film%20even%20while%20flirting%20with%20the%20supernatural%20roots%20its%20horrors%20in%20the%20plausible.%20The%20palazzo%2C%20where%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20film%20unfolds%2C%20is%20said%20to%20have%20been%20an%20erstwhile%20children%E2%80%99s%20hospital%20%E2%80%93%20where%20doctors%20and%20nurses%20are%20believed%20to%20have%20locked%20and%20abandoned%20their%20patients%2C%20during%20the%20plague.%20A%20character%20recounts%20the%20terror%20he%20witnessed%20in%20the%20Second%20World%20War%20%E2%80%93%20leaving%20them%20with%20a%20permanent%20case%20of%20%E2%80%9CBattle%20Fever%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20making%20everyone%20jumpy%20during%20social%20gatherings%20and%20lash%20out%20during%20the%20most%20unexpected%20moments.%20Another%20character%20casually%20recounts%20how%20when%20they%20bumped%20into%20a%20battalion%20and%20mentally%20prepared%20to%20die%2C%20instead%20finding%20refuge%20in%20a%20Hollywood%20classic%20and%20watching%20it%20on%20repeat%20with%20friendly%20soldiers%20for%20a%20whole%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20boils%20down%20to%20a%20splendid%20thesis%20that%20even%20though%20it%20is%20Branagh%E2%80%99s%20third%20film%20in%20a%20lucrative%20franchise%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20possible%20to%20locate%20its%20personality.%20For%20a%20film%20busting%20myths%20about%20ghosts%20and%20spirits%2C%20maybe%20this%20is%20one%20way%20to%20exorcise%20the%20threat%20of%20looming%20studios.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694871026000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F16171626%2Fimage-1321.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fwith-a-haunting-in-venice-the-director-goes-in-more-for-mood-and-atmosphere-rather-than-glamour%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Agatha%20Christie%E2%80%99s%20novel%20gets%20the%20full%20gothic%20treatment%20in%20the%20city%20of%20canals.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fwith-a-haunting-in-venice-the-director-goes-in-more-for-mood-and-atmosphere-rather-than-glamour%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Auditors%20should%20embrace%20technology%2C%20contribute%20to%20nation%20building%3A%20FM%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694870494000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-08%2F25%2Ffull%2F1692962966-5423.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fauditors-should-embrace-technology-contribute-to-nation-building-fm-123091600710_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Finance%20and%20Corporate%20Affairs%20Minister%20remarked%20that%20the%20country%20has%20progressed%20at%20many%20levels%20in%20the%20last%2020-25%20years%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fauditors-should-embrace-technology-contribute-to-nation-building-fm-123091600710_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fauditors-should-embrace-technology-contribute-to-nation-building-fm-123091600710_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fauditors-should-embrace-technology-contribute-to-nation-building-fm-123091600710_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20INDIA%20Bloc%20Defends%20TV%20Anchor%20Boycott%20List%20as%20'Non-Cooperation'%2C%20BJP%20Calls%20it%20'Emergency'%20Mindset%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F01145236%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-01-at-1.39.01-PM-e1693560384596.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20INDIA%20bloc%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20draw%20up%20a%20list%20of%2014%20news%20anchors%20on%20whose%20TV%20shows%20their%20representatives%20will%20not%20participate%20has%20ignited%20a%20debate%20on%20free%20speech%20with%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20invoking%20the%20Emergency%20and%20accusing%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20of%20%E2%80%9Cgagging%20the%20media%20for%20speaking%20the%20truth%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20September%2014%2C%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20released%20a%20list%20of%2014%20news%20anchors%20and%20said%20that%20their%20representatives%20will%20not%20be%20sent%20to%20their%20respective%20shows%20and%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20named%20Aditi%20Tyagi%20(Bharat%20Express)%2C%20Aman%20Chopra%20(News18%20India)%2C%20Amish%20Devgan%20(News18%20India)%2C%20Anand%20Narasimhan%20(CNN%20News%2018)%2C%20Arnab%20Goswami%20(Republic%20TV)%2C%20Ashok%20Shrivastav%20(DD%20News)%2C%20Chitra%20Tripathi%20(Aaj%20Tak)%2C%20Gaurav%20Sawant%20(India%20Today)%2C%20Navika%20Kumar%20(Times%20Now)%2C%20Prachi%20Parashar%20(India%20TV)%2C%20Rubika%20Liaquat%20(Bharat%2024)%2C%20Shiv%20Aroor%20(India%20Today)%2C%20Sudhir%20Chaudhary%20(Aaj%20Tak)%2C%20and%20Sushant%20Sinha%20(Times%20Now%20Navbharat).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20was%20released%20a%20day%20after%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20in%20its%20first%20coordination%20committee%20meeting%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20decided%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-alliance-to-boycott-tv-shows-that-conduct-inflammatory-debates%5C%22%3Elist%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20news%20anchors%20whose%20shows%20will%20be%20boycotted%20by%20the%20member%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-alliance-to-boycott-tv-shows-that-conduct-inflammatory-debates%5C%22%3EIndia%20Alliance%20to%20Boycott%20TV%20Shows%20That%20%E2%80%98Conduct%20Inflammatory%20Debates%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20Saturday%2C%20September%2016%2C%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20Congress%20spokesperson%20Pawan%20Khera%20said%20that%20the%20move%20to%20not%20participate%20in%20these%20shows%20was%20not%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cboycott%E2%80%9D%20but%20instead%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cnon-cooperation%20movement%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20not%20banned%2C%20boycotted%20or%20blacklisted%20anyone.%20This%20is%20a%20non-cooperation%20movement%2C%20we%20will%20not%20cooperate%20with%20anyone%20spreading%20hatred%20in%20the%20society.%20We%20are%20not%20stopping%20them%20from%20spreading%20hatred.%20You%20want%20to%20spread%20hatred%2C%20go%20ahead%20and%20do%20it.%20You%20have%20the%20freedom%20to%20do%20it.%20We%20also%20have%20the%20freedom%20not%20to%20be%20partners%20in%20that%20crime.%20They%20are%20not%20our%20enemies.%20We%20do%20not%20hate%20any%20of%20these%20friends%20of%20ours%20in%20the%20media.%20They%20may%20have%20their%20compulsions.%20And%20nothing%20is%20permanent%2C%20if%20tomorrow%20they%20realise%20that%20what%20they%20were%20doing%20is%20not%20good%20for%20India%2C%20not%20good%20for%20the%20society%20we%20are%20all%20together%20in%20this%2C%20we%20will%20again%20start%20attending%20their%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDo%20not%20call%20it%20a%20ban.%20This%20can%20be%20called%20a%20non-cooperation%20movement.%20We%20are%20using%20a%20Gandhian%20method%20to%20exercise%20our%20freedom%20to%20not%20walk%20on%20those%20roads%20on%20which%20we%20are%20hurled%20garbage.%20We%20are%20just%20exercising%20our%20freedom%20and%20nothing%20else.%20All%20parties%20who%20are%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20we%20have%20to%20change%20our%20path%20and%20we%20will%20not%20be%20a%20part%20of%20this.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20ban%20or%20a%20boycott%20or%20a%20blacklist%2C%20this%20is%20a%20non-cooperation%20movement.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20the%20alliance%20took%20shape%20in%20June%2C%20the%20leaders%20have%20spoken%20about%20the%20%E2%80%9Cunprecedented%20hostility%E2%80%9D%20faced%20by%20opposition%20parties%20during%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20regime.%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20had%20indicated%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20Mumbai%20meetings%20that%20a%20strategy%20to%20counter%20propagandist%20media%20will%20be%20discussed%20among%20INDIA%20bloc%20constituents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMindset%20of%20%E2%80%98Emergency%E2%80%99%2C%20says%20BJP%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20bloc%E2%80%99s%20move%20has%20evoked%20sharp%20criticism%20from%20the%20BJP%20which%20has%20accused%20the%20alliance%20of%20displaying%20a%20mindset%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20Emergency%20under%20former%20prime%20minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20when%20the%20freedom%20of%20the%20press%20was%20curtailed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20on%20Thursday%20night%2C%20the%20BJP%20said%20that%20it%20severely%20opposes%20%E2%80%9Csuch%20derogatory%20mentality%20which%20hinders%20freedom%20of%20expression%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20decision%20of%20political%20parties%20which%20are%20part%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98ghamandiya%E2%80%99%20alliance%20to%20boycott%20some%20journalists%20shows%20their%20mentality%20of%20the%20time%20of%20repressive%20Emergency.%20Today%20also%20the%20%E2%80%98ghamandiya%E2%80%99%20alliance%20is%20working%20with%20the%20same%20mindset%20of%20Emergency%20and%20vengeance%20against%20the%20media.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CINDIA%20alliance%20giving%20direct%20threat%20to%20the%20media%20is%20like%20gagging%20the%20media%20for%20speaking%20the%20truth.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20Friday%2C%20BJP%20spokesperson%20Sambit%20Patra%20in%20New%20Delhi%20said%20that%20the%20names%20released%20by%20the%20opposition%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Chit%20list.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWas%20this%20a%20boycott%20list%20or%20a%20target%20list%3F%20Are%20they%20just%20being%20boycotting%20or%20are%20they%20being%20targeted%3F%20This%20is%20a%20hit%20list.%20There%20are%20some%20journalists%20who%20do%20not%20conduct%20debates%20so%20how%20will%20you%20send%20guests%20there%3F%20So%20why%20have%20their%20names%20been%20included%3F%20To%20target%20them.%20They%20will%20file%20FIRs%20against%20them%20and%20target%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20itself%20had%2C%20however%2C%20boycotted%20NDTV%20in%202014%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20alleged%20%E2%80%9Cmanufactured%20tweet.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bjp.org%2Fpressreleases%2Fpress-boycott-ndtv%5C%22%3Epress%20release%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethe%20party%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CTweet%20being%20manufactured%20by%20a%20channel%20in%20order%20to%20hurt%20BJP%20is%20unprecedented.%20BJP%20therefore%20has%20decided%20to%20keep%20away%20from%20panel%20discussions%20of%20NDTV%20for%20present.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENDTV%20had%20erroneously%20reported%20a%20tweet%20by%20Sushma%20Swaraj%20saying%20that%20if%20there%20is%20a%20Modi%20wave%20in%20India%2C%20then%20why%20is%20he%20(Modi)%20looking%20for%20a%20safe%20seat%20in%20UP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Swaraj%E2%80%99s%20official%20handle%20had%20not%20made%20any%20such%20tweet%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F658110%2Fbjp-decides-to-boycott-ndtv-over-erroneous-tweet%5C%22%3E%20reported%20Scroll.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20the%20official%20account%20of%20the%20channel%20and%20then%20senior%20editor%20Barkha%20Dutt%20apologised%20for%20the%20error.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Dangerous%20precedent%2C%E2%80%99%20says%20NBDA%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20move%20to%20release%20the%20list%20of%20news%20anchors%20has%20also%20been%20criticised%20by%20the%20New%20Broadcasters%20and%20Digital%20Association%20(NBDA).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20on%20Thursday%2C%20the%20NBDA%20said%20that%20it%20is%20deeply%20anguished%20and%20concerned%20by%20the%20decision%20taken%20by%20the%20INDIA%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20decision%20taken%20by%20the%20INDIA%20media%20committee%20sets%20a%20dangerous%20precedent.%20The%20ban%20on%20representatives%20of%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20from%20participating%20in%20TV%20news%20shows%20anchored%20by%20some%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20top%20TV%20News%20personalities%20goes%20against%20the%20ethos%20of%20democracy.%20It%20betokens%20intolerance%20and%20imperils%20press%20freedom.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%20invoking%20the%20Emergency%2C%20the%20NBDA%20said%20that%20it%20takes%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20nation%20back%20to%20the%20Emergency%20era%2C%20when%20the%20press%20was%20gagged%20and%20independent%20opinions%20and%20voices%20were%20crushed%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Boycott%20is%20a%20badge%20of%20honour%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20some%20of%20the%20TV%20anchors%20mentioned%20in%20the%20list%20have%20taken%20to%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20and%20spoken%20out%20against%20their%20names%20being%20included%20in%20the%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAman%20Chopra%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20X%20wrote%20that%20a%20boycott%20is%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbiggest%20badge%20of%20honour%20for%20a%20journalist%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E0%A4%B5%E0%A5%88%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%A6%20%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20interview%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%AC%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A6%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%88%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%87%E0%A4%B8%20%E0%A4%AC%E0%A5%89%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%89%E0%A4%9F%20%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%AC%E0%A5%88%E0%A4%9C%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%8B%20%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B5%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%9A%E0%A4%B2%20%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%82%E0%A4%81%20%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B2%20%E0%A4%AA%E0%A5%82%E0%A4%9B%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%AD%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%95%20%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%80%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%9B%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%A1%E0%A4%BC%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%88%E0%A5%A4%20%E0%A4%AC%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%B