%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329864%2Fiit-delhi-grads-siddhant-jain-vibhav-sinha-founded-vdocipher-data-encryption-video-piracy-security%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20be%20a%20teacher%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20became%20a%20government%20school%20teacher%20when%20I%20was%2019.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20do%20my%20graduation%20then%20as%20I%20wanted%20to%20start%20teaching%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20could.%20All%20I%20did%20was%20complete%20the%20teachers%E2%80%99%20training%20programme%20and%20appear%20for%20its%20qualifying%20exam%2C%E2%80%9D%20Archana%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%205%20September%202023%2C%20she%20received%20the%20National%20Teachers%20Award%20from%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20at%20the%20Vigyan%20Bhawan%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20These%20awards%20are%20conferred%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Education%20to%20the%20finest%20school%20teachers%20in%20the%20country%20who%20have%20improved%20the%20quality%20of%20education%20and%20brought%20about%20change%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20their%20students.%20This%20award%20was%20the%20culmination%20of%20her%20hard%20work%20and%20dedication%20towards%20the%20teaching%20profession.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2042-year-old%20headmistress%20first%20started%20as%20a%20primary%20school%20class%20teacher%20here%20in%20Telangana.%20From%20a%20non-descript%20centre%20of%20learning%20with%20just%20a%20few%20students%2C%20this%20educator%20has%20transformed%20the%20school%20into%20a%20mecca%20of%20learning%2C%20offering%20holistic%20growth%20through%20a%20variety%20of%20extra-curricular%20activities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20seeds%20of%20change%20were%20sown%20in%20Archana%E2%80%99s%20mind%20at%20home.%20She%20saw%20her%20grandfather%2C%20a%20teacher%2C%20serve%20students.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20grandfather%20would%20teach%20a%20lot%20of%20tribal%20students.%20He%20used%20to%20teach%20them%20at%20our%20house%20and%20helped%20them%20in%20their%20higher%20studies.%20I%20aspired%20to%20be%20like%20him%20and%20help%20students%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20teacher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhere%20it%20all%20began%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20862px)%20100vw%2C%20862px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-10-at-11.25.39-1694697068.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22862%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Archana%20Nooguri%20with%20the%20students%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-10-at-11.25.39-1694697068.jpeg%20862w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-10-at-11.25.39-1694697068-300x214.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-10-at-11.25.39-1694697068-500x356.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-10-at-11.25.39-1694697068-768x547.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-10-at-11.25.39-1694697068-150x107.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329945%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22614%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EArchana%20Nooguri%20with%20her%20students.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ERebbenapally%2C%20where%20the%20school%20is%20located%2C%20faces%20a%20lot%20of%20challenges%20in%20terms%20of%20infrastructure%2C%20access%20to%20education%2C%20and%20healthcare%20to%20name%20a%20few.%20When%20Archana%20joined%20the%20school%20in%20November%202000%2C%20it%20had%20just%2034%20students.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20Mancherial%20district%2C%20she%20was%20acquainted%20with%20the%20troubles%20faced%20by%20the%20locals%20and%20why%20they%20weren%E2%80%99t%20sending%20their%20children%20to%20the%20school.%20She%20wanted%20to%20use%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F322088%2Fkerala-teacher-gives-free-upsc-coaching-to-aspirants-with-disabilities%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etransformative%20power%20of%20education%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20these%20students%20attend%20school%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20a%20few%20tribal%20hamlets%20in%20this%20village.%20The%20occupation%20of%20the%20residents%20is%20to%20collect%20raw%20materials%20from%20the%20forest.%20There%20are%20no%20transport%20facilities%20to%20these%20hamlets%20as%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20a%20%3Cem%3Epucca%3C%2Fem%3E%20road.%20When%20I%20joined%2C%20my%20first%20mission%20was%20to%20ensure%20that%20these%20children%20come%20to%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Archana%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArchana%20embarked%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20get%20those%20children%20to%20school.%20She%20started%20visiting%20those%20tribal%20hamlets%20and%20spoke%20to%20the%20parents.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20proper%20houses%20or%20even%20clothes%20to%20wear.%20They%20were%20not%20aware%20of%20the%20school%20as%20no%20one%20from%20there%20was%20enrolled.%20I%20visited%20them%20daily%20for%2015%20days%20to%20convince%20them.%20I%20told%20them%20how%20essential%20education%20is%20and%20how%20it%20can%20help%20their%20children%20lead%20a%20better%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Archana.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20exalted%20the%20benefits%20of%20education%20and%20the%20change%20it%20enables.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20show%20them%20videos%20of%20people%20who%20came%20from%20similar%20backgrounds%20and%20are%20in%20a%20good%20position%20today.%20Through%20education%2C%20they%20were%20able%20to%20transform%20their%20lives.%20I%20urged%20these%20parents%20to%20give%20their%20children%20the%20same%20opportunity%20to%20progress%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMany%20Problems%20Laced%20The%20Journey%20to%20Success%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Farchana-1694697763.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Archana%20received%20the%20National%20Award%20for%20Teachers%202023%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Farchana-1694697763.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Farchana-1694697763-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Farchana-1694697763-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Farchana-1694697763-768x512.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Farchana-1694697763-150x100.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Farchana-1694697763-272x182.jpeg%20272w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329966%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EArchana%20received%20the%20National%20Award%20for%20Teachers%202023%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EArchana%20was%20able%20to%20convince%20the%20parents%20and%20the%20children%20soon%20started%20coming%20to%20school.%20However%2C%20she%20soon%20started%20seeing%20students%20drop%20out.%20On%20enquiry%2C%20she%20realised%20that%20transportation%20was%20a%20major%20challenge.%20How%20would%20these%20children%20come%20to%20the%20school%20which%20was%20over%205%20km%20away%20with%20just%20a%20%3Cem%3Ekaccha%20%3C%2Fem%3Eroad%20leading%20to%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20solve%20this%20problem%2C%20Archana%20arranged%20an%20auto%20to%20pick%20up%20and%20drop%20off%20the%20students%20daily%2C%20at%20her%20own%20expense.%20Through%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327999%2Famerican-english-teacher-elizabeth-keyton-started-elikutty-to-learn-and-teach-malayalam-instagram%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etireless%20efforts%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20ensure%20that%20the%20tribal%20students%20in%20the%20village%20are%20educated%2C%20she%20has%20increased%20the%20strength%20to%20275%20students%20today%2C%20with%20103%20being%20girls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20this%2C%20she%20also%20worked%20on%20developing%20the%20school%20infrastructure.%20For%20this%2C%20she%20enlisted%20the%20help%20of%20a%20former%20student%20of%20her%20school%2C%20Rajendra%20Prasad%2C%20who%20now%20lives%20abroad.%20NGOs%20like%20Bring%20a%20Smile%20Foundation%2C%20Padmavati%20Charitable%20Trust%20and%20local%20politicians%20also%20joined%20hands%20to%20support%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20able%20to%20procure%20a%20borewell%2C%20purified%20water%20plant%2C%20furniture%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20built%20a%20beautiful%20library%20with%201000%20books%2C%20through%20their%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRajendra%20has%20helped%20tremendously%20in%20the%20growth%20of%20the%20school.%20He%20is%20the%20person%20through%20whom%20we%20got%20most%20of%20the%20donations.%20The%20Washington%20Telangana%20Association%20(WATA)%20helped%20us%20get%2040%20benches%20for%20the%20school%20because%20of%20his%20efforts.%20A%20local%20MLA%20installed%20the%20borewell%20and%20an%20RO%20plant%20in%20the%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20learning%20more%20fun%2C%20through%20digital%20technology%20and%20the%20central%20government%E2%80%99s%20Information%20and%20Communication%20Technology%20(ICT)%20initiative%2C%20she%20procured%20five%20computers%2C%20two%20LED%20projectors%20and%20two%20additional%20classrooms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ICT%20Information%20and%20Communication%20Technology%20School%20Scheme%20was%20launched%20in%20December%202004%20to%20provide%20opportunities%20to%20secondary%20stage%20students%20to%20mainly%20build%20their%20capacity%20on%20ICT%20skills%20and%20make%20them%20learn%20through%20the%20computer-aided%20learning%20process.%20She%20proudly%20states%20that%20her%20students%20are%20now%20able%20to%20use%20computers%20proficiently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20living%20in%20an%20era%20of%20globalisation.%20To%20be%20a%20global%20citizen%2C%20digital%20education%20is%20a%20must.%20I%20want%20my%20students%20to%20know%20how%20to%20operate%20computers%20well%20and%20therefore%2C%20am%20exposing%20them%20to%20the%20technology%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20headmistress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGiving%20holistic%20education%20a%20must%20for%20this%20school%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESmt.%20Archana%20Nooguri%2C%20a%20National%20Awardee%20Teacher%202023%20from%20Telangana%2C%20works%20on%20improving%20enrolment%20rates%20%26amp%3B%20reducing%20dropouts.%20She%20develops%20low-cost%20teaching-learning%20material.%20She%20involved%20the%20community%20in%20setting%20up%20water%20purification%20plant%2C%20library%20etc.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FOurTeachersOurPrerna%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23OurTeachersOurPrerna%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FeU7InH6xFN%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FeU7InH6xFN%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Ministry%20of%20Education%20(%40EduMinOfIndia)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEduMinOfIndia%2Fstatus%2F1699030560587608210%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%205%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20more%20than%20100%20girl%20students%2C%20Archana%20wanted%20them%20to%20learn%20self-defence.%20