.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Famravati-2-1694610828-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Famravati-2-1694610828-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329822%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EOn%207%20March%2C%202023%2C%20Ravindra%20was%20invited%20to%20address%20189%20trainees.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFarmers%20make%20a%20significant%20contribution%20to%20the%20district%E2%80%99s%20productivity.%20So%20IAS%20officers%20should%20be%20aware%20of%20their%20real-life%20challenges%20and%20understand%20what%20farmers%20expect%20from%20them%20when%20they%20are%20posted%20in%20the%20districts.%20I%20got%20an%20opportunity%20to%20help%20the%20trainees%20understand%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarting%20with%20just%20100%20poultry%20hens%2C%20Ravindra%20now%20owns%201.8%20lakh%20hens%20on%20his%2050-acre%20farm%20in%20Amravati.%20We%20sat%20down%20with%20him%20to%20understand%20his%20experiences%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F82739%2Fifarm-integrated-aquaponics-poultry-kerala-veterinary-university%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epoultry%20farmer%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20how%20he%20managed%20to%20achieve%20this%20feat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESetting%20up%20business%20at%2016%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20overcome%20financial%20constraints%2C%20Ravindra%20worked%20at%20a%20chemist%E2%80%99s%20store%20that%20would%20earn%20him%20Rs%205%20per%20day.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20did%20not%20own%20any%20ancestral%20land.%20Our%20financial%20condition%20was%20very%20poor.%20I%20remember%20going%20to%20college%20on%20foot%20as%20I%20did%20not%20have%20a%20bicycle.%20I%20used%20to%20repair%20old%20torn%20clothes%20to%20wear%20to%20college%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.