20up%20a%20recycling%20plant%20on%20the%20campus.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20plant%20recycles%20as%20much%20plastic%20that%20is%20recyclable%20and%20converts%20them%20into%20eco-bricks.%20Our%20kids%20learn%20how%20to%20convert%20plastic%20into%20bricks%20and%20work%20in%20the%20plant%20after%20school.%20We%20pay%20them%20for%20that%20too.%20This%20way%20they%20get%20to%20learn%20an%20extra%20skill%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20eco-bricks%20are%20then%20used%20in%20smaller%20constructions%20in%20and%20around%20the%20school.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20also%20using%20a%20machine%20from%20the%20Netherlands.%20The%20machine%20upcycles%20the%20plastic%20into%20things%20of%20use.%20We%20have%20to%20put%20the%20melted%20plastic%20in%20different%20moulds%20and%20the%20machine%20converts%20it%20into%20pots%2C%20planters%2C%20keyrings%2C%20earnings%20etc%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEuroschool-image-5-1694607289.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEuroschool-image-5-1694607289.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEuroschool-image-5-1694607289-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEuroschool-image-5-1694607289-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEuroschool-image-5-1694607289-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEuroschool-image-5-1694607289-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329788%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20eco-bricks%20are%20then%20used%20in%20smaller%20constructions%20in%20and%20around%20the%20school.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Parmita%20Sarma%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20only%20a%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325564%2Fthe-disposal-company-bhagyashree-bhansali-waste-plastic-credit-recycle-mumbai-delhi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20few%20types%20of%20plastic%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20we%20can%20use%20around%20children%20and%20the%20rest%20we%20ship%20to%20other%20recycling%20companies%2C%E2%80%9D%20informs%20Mazin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWatching%20the%20success%20of%20their%20school%2C%20the%20couple%20decided%20to%20expand%20their%20curriculum.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20collaborated%20with%20a%20residential%20school%20in%20Delhi%20for%20orphans%20and%20our%20curriculum%20worked%20successfully%20with%20them.%20Although%20we%20wanted%20to%20expand%20it%20to%20more%20schools%20in%20Delhi%2C%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20put%20our%20plans%20on%20hold%20and%20we%20had%20to%20call%20our%20team%20back%20to%20Assam%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20road%20ahead%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20the%20couple%20reached%20out%20to%20more%20schools%20in%20Assam%20and%20signed%20an%20MoU%20with%20the%20state%20government%20to%20replicate%20their%20educational%20model%20in%20five%20government%20schools.%20Currently%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20implemented%20this%20model%20in%2014%20schools%20in%20Assam%20and%20are%20hoping%20to%20reach%20200%20more%20by%20the%20end%20of%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20was%20contacted%20by%20the%20Assan%20government%20to%20assist%20them%20in%20the%20Swachh%20Bharat%20Mission.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB0gDftpHSrO%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm