lement-caption%5C%22%3EDevra%20prides%20itself%20on%20traditional%20Udaipur%20culture%20and%20authentic%20delicacies%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Jyoti%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20guests%20at%20the%20housewarming%20lunch%20in%202004%20included%20the%20couple%E2%80%99s%20parents%20and%20all%20the%20craftsmen%20who%20had%20been%20a%20part%20of%20their%20journey.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20the%20assurance%20that%20even%20if%20I%20want%20to%20make%2010%20more%20houses%2C%20these%20people%20will%20support%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jyoti%20adds%2C%20laughing.%20Such%20is%20the%20strength%20of%20their%20bond.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20majesty%20of%20Udaipur%E2%80%99s%20lands%20comes%20alive%20with%20this%20property%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20started%20with%20three%20rooms%20is%20now%20a%2010-bedroom%20heritage%20homestay%20made%20of%20Rajasthani%20stone%2C%20bang%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20lush%20fields%20and%20farms.%20However%2C%20this%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20state%20of%20the%20land%20in%201994.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJyoti%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20visited%20the%20land%20for%20the%20first%20time%20all%20we%20saw%20was%20cactus.%20The%20land%20did%20not%20support%20the%20growth%20of%20anything%20else.%E2%80%9D%20However%2C%20a%20solution%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298965%2Fdelhi-professiors-turn-traditional-houses-into-homestays-boost-sustainable-tourism-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etransform%20the%20land%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20a%20viable%20farm%20came%20in%20the%20form%20of%20the%20Pichola%20Lake%20in%20Udaipur.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20bringing%20in%20soil%20from%20the%20lake%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%20While%20Jyoti%20succeeded%20in%20doing%20this%20at%20the%20time%2C%20today%20it%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20an%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20the%20Rajasthan%20Lake%20Protection%20and%20Conservation%20Authority%20passed%20a%20proposal%20that%20put%20three%20lakes%20in%20Udaipur%20under%20a%20prohibited%20zone%2C%20thus%20curbing%20desilting%20or%20soil%20extraction%20activities%20in%20them.%20Pichola%20Lake%20was%20one%20of%20these.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C20%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20ban%20that%20now%20exists%20over%20removing%20soil%20from%20the%20lake%20was%20not%20there.%20So%2C%20when%20the%20lake%20would%20dry%20up%20in%20summer%20up%20to%20its%20middle%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20good%20quality%20loamy%20soil%20would%20be%20left%20behind.%20This%20soil%2C%20filled%20with%20minerals%20and%20nutrients%2C%20is%20perfect%20for%20growing%20plants.%20We%20started%20bringing%20it%20to%20the%20land%20to%20grow%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311053%2Fdushyant-vashisht-turned-cottage-to-sustainable-homestay-bir-terraces-uttarakhand-tourism%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eour%20first%20trees%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F027f03fee490484988a3eef5325fc6e9-1694177357.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%20Devra%20guests%20are%20taken%20to%20experience%20the%20local%20culture%20and%20the%20nearby%20villages%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F027f03fee490484988a3eef5325fc6e9-1694177357.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F027f03fee490484988a3eef5325fc6e9-1694177357-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F027f03fee490484988a3eef5325fc6e9-1694177357-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F027f03fee490484988a3eef5325fc6e9-1694177357-15