0by%20unorganised%20players%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Balachander%20(46)%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20Chennai%2C%20people%20are%20dependent%20on%20water%20tanks%20for%20their%20daily%20water%20needs%20as%20the%20groundwater%20is%20very%20polluted%20or%20it%20is%20so%20saline%20that%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20use.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20day%2C%20more%20than%2025%20lakh%20cans%20of%2020-litre%20capacity%20are%20sold%20in%20Chennai.%20Even%20the%20poorest%20here%20are%20dependent%20on%20water%20cans%20that%20cost%20Rs%2035-45.%20But%20no%20one%20really%20knows%20the%20quality%20of%20water%20and%20of%20these%20cans.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20plastic%20water%20cans%20are%20also%20overused.%20You%20are%20not%20supposed%20to%20reuse%20these%20water%20cans%20beyond%20a%20certain%20extent%20after%20which%2C%20they%20start%20to%20lose%20their%20transparency.%20But%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20cans%20you%20see%20in%20the%20market%20will%20be%20completely%20clouded%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20happens%20due%20to%20the%20cans%20being%20left%20under%20the%20sun.%20The%20UV%20rays%20break%20the%20plastic%20into%20smaller%20particles%20which%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20sheds%20copious%20amounts%20of%20microplastics%20into%20the%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fbookwater-1-1694173056.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20company%20allows%20users%20to%20scan%20the%20QR%20code%20on%20its%20water%20cans%20and%20get%20details%20about%20the%20quality%20of%20cans.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fbookwater-1-169