ly%20questions%20it.%20%E2%80%9CWill%20you%20drink%20Ganga%20river%E2%80%99s%20water%20from%20a%20bathroom%20bucket%3F%20No.%20Likewise%2C%20we%20have%20accepted%20that%20these%20dirty%20plastic%20water%20cans%20are%20good.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20brothers%20wanted%20to%20use%20IoT%20tech%20to%20solve%20these%20problems%20and%20that%20is%20when%20their%20%E2%80%9Cconnected%20cans%E2%80%9D%20concept%20was%20born.%20In%202020%2C%20the%20siblings%20launched%20BookWater%20and%20were%20joined%20by%20Sameer%20and%20Hariharan%20about%20a%20year%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20does%20the%20QR%20do%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20the%20brothers%20manufacture%20ISI%20(Indian%20Standards%20Institution)-rated%20plastic%20cans%20where%20they%20stick%20a%20QR%20code%20on%20every%20can.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20IoT%20sensors%20in%20the%20copackers%E2%80%99%20locations.%20Our%20sensors%20monitor%20the%20quality%20of%20water%20and%20where%20it%20is%20filled.%20If%20you%20order%20a%20can%20through%20the%20BookWater%20app%2C%20you%20can%20scan%20the%20QR%20code%20and%20quality%20reports%20will%20be%20visible%20to%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bharath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fbookwater-3-1694173807.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22When%20the%20cans%20are%20left%20under%20the%20sun%2C%20the%20UV%20rays%20break%20the%20plastic%20particles%20and%20shed%20copious%20amounts%20of%20microplastics%20into%20the%20water.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fbookwater-3-1694173807.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fbookwater-3-1694173807-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fbookwater-3-1694173807-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fbookwater-3-1694173807-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fbookwater-3-1694173807-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329459%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWhen%20the%20cans%20are%20left%20under%20the%20sun%2C%20the%20UV%20rays%20break%20the%20plastic%20particles%20and%20shed%20copious%20amounts%20of%20microplastics%20into%20the%20water.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20code%20then%20allows%20you%20to%20track%20the%20movement%20of%20the%20can%20from%20the%20copacker%20to%20the%20customer%20location.%20It%20tells%20all%20the%20quality%20parameters%20%E2%80%93%20right%20from%20how%20many%20times%20the%20can%20has%20been%20reused%2C%20the%20manufacturing%20date%20of%20the%20can%2C%20calcium%2C%20magnesium%2C%20TDS%20(Total%20Dissolved%20Solids)%2C%20to%20the%20PH-levels%20of%20the%20water%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBala%20says%20that%20every%20can%20is%20scanned%20till%20it%20is%20upcycled.%20After%20using%20the%20can%20up%20to%2030%20times%2C%20the%20startup%20upcycles%20it%20into%20useful%20products%20like%20t-shirts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%2C%20they%20have%20collaborated%20with%20companies%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F319912%2Ftamil-nadu-father-son-duo-senthil-kumar-recycle-plastic-bottles-into-sustainable-clothes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEcoline%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20recycles%20plastic%20bottles%20into%20sustainable%20clothing%20such%20as%20jackets%2C%20blazers%2C%20T-shirts%2C%20and%20bottoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20BookWater%20is%20catering%20to%203%2C000%20users%20across%20Chennai%20but%20aims%20to%20expand%20services%20to%20Karnataka